Name: IKEA
HQ Location: Netherlands, South Holland, Delft, 1 Olof Palmestraat, 2616
Company description: IKEA is a global leader in home furnishings, dedicated to creating a better everyday life for the many people by offering a wide range of well-designed, functional, and affordable products. Founded in 1943 in Sweden, the company specializes in ready-to-assemble furniture, kitchen solutions, and home accessories that cater to diverse customer needs and preferences. IKEA's mission emphasizes sustainability and social responsibility, focusing on providing accessible and stylish solutions for home living while promoting a positive impact on both people and the planet. The company's vision for 2030 aims to regenerate resources, protect ecosystems, and improve biodiversity, with a commitment to using only responsibly sourced renewable or recycled materials in its offerings. IKEA serves a diverse clientele, including families, young professionals, and students, who seek practical home solutions at competitive prices. The company partners with over 1,600 suppliers and manufacturers worldwide to ensure quality and sustainability throughout its value chain, while also engaging with social businesses to empower marginalized communities and promote ethical practices. With a focus on circularity, IKEA is transforming its business model to ensure that all products are designed for reuse, refurbishment, and recycling by 2030. Through initiatives like the SOLSTRÅLE home solar offer and various biodiversity projects, IKEA strives to inspire and enable customers to live healthier, more sustainable lives. The company actively engages with communities and stakeholders to drive positive social impact, addressing critical issues such as climate change and human rights. By championing environmental stewardship and promoting equality, diversity, and inclusion, IKEA continues to innovate and adapt to meet the evolving needs of its customers while maintaining its commitment to affordability and accessibility.

Name: Mondo Convenienza
Company description: Mondo Convenienza is a leading Italian company that has been specializing in affordable furniture and home decor for over 40 years, making quality design accessible to millions of families. Founded in Civitavecchia in 1985, the company has expanded significantly, operating 47 retail locations and 42 logistics centers across Italy, as well as 3 stores and 2 hubs in Spain. With a dedicated workforce of 4,500 employees, Mondo Convenienza is committed to providing a tailored shopping experience through its "Dolce Casa" service and various digital channels. The company's mission is to offer stylish and affordable home furnishings, catering to a diverse clientele that includes budget-conscious consumers, families, and individuals looking to enhance their living spaces with modern and functional products. Mondo Convenienza prides itself on its strong relationships with suppliers, with 80% being Italian, which underscores its commitment to supporting local businesses and fostering community engagement. The company emphasizes continuous innovation and a forward-looking vision, ensuring that it remains at the forefront of the furniture industry. Customer satisfaction is a top priority, and Mondo Convenienza offers multiple communication channels for support, including live chat, phone consultations, and in-store assistance. Its partnerships and community initiatives reflect a commitment to inclusivity and providing opportunities for all. With a focus on quality and value, Mondo Convenienza aims to be the leading choice for consumers seeking comprehensive home furnishing solutions that combine style, functionality, and affordability.

Name: Conforama España
HQ Location: Spain, Catalonia, El Prat De Llobregat, 1-3 Avenida Baix Llobregat, 08820
Company description: Conforama España es una compañía multinacional líder en el equipamiento del hogar, con más de 2500 empleados y 57 tiendas en la península ibérica y las islas. Su misión es hacer que el confort sea accesible para todos sus clientes, satisfaciendo plenamente sus expectativas a través de una oferta variada de mobiliario y decoración. La empresa se caracteriza por su ambiente de trabajo dinámico y positivo, donde el talento y la calidad humana son considerados sus principales valores. Conforama busca constantemente personas con orientación al cliente y habilidades en el montaje de muebles, ofreciendo oportunidades de crecimiento y desarrollo profesional. Su mercado objetivo incluye a familias y particulares que buscan soluciones de mobiliario asequibles y de calidad para sus hogares.

Name: BHG Finland
Company description: BHG Finland is a leading player in the Nordic consumer e-commerce landscape, operating under the umbrella of BHG Group AB, one of Europe's largest online retailers. The company specializes in three primary business units: Home Improvement, Value Home, and Premium Living, offering an extensive selection of approximately 1.7 million products, including DIY supplies, furniture, and home furnishings. BHG Finland's mission is to simplify the lives of its customers, encapsulated in its vision, "We make living easy!" This commitment drives the company to provide a comprehensive product portfolio at competitive prices, ensuring exceptional online customer experiences and professional services. With a strong online presence, BHG serves a diverse clientele across the Nordic region, including individual consumers and businesses, while also expanding its reach into European and Asian markets. The company operates over 100 online platforms, featuring well-known brands like Bygghemma and Nordic Nest, and collaborates with reputable external brands such as Bosch and Husqvarna to enhance its offerings. BHG Finland is dedicated to sustainability and operational efficiency, focusing on ethical supply chains and high standards of product safety and quality. The company's strategic vision emphasizes profitable growth through organic expansion and strategic acquisitions, with a net sales target of SEK 20 billion in the medium term. BHG Finland aims to strengthen its leadership position in the premium segment of the home furnishings industry while adapting to changing consumer behaviors and market conditions. By continuously seeking to streamline operations and consolidate its market presence, BHG is well-positioned for long-term growth and success in the evolving e-commerce landscape.

Name: Dänisches Bettenlager
Company description: Dänisches Bettenlager, auch bekannt als JYSK, ist ein international tätiges Einzelhandelsunternehmen, das sich auf den Verkauf von Möbeln, Matratzen, Heimtextilien und Wohnaccessoires spezialisiert hat. Gegründet 1979 in Dänemark, verfolgt das Unternehmen die Mission, hochwertige Produkte zu einem dauerhaft niedrigen Preis anzubieten und dabei ein hervorragendes Einkaufserlebnis zu gewährleisten. Mit über 3.000 Filialen weltweit bedient JYSK eine breite Zielgruppe, die sowohl Privatkunden als auch Geschäftskunden umfasst. Das Unternehmen legt großen Wert auf die Entwicklung seiner Mitarbeiter und bietet zahlreiche Aufstiegsmöglichkeiten sowie ein positives Arbeitsumfeld.  Dänisches Bettenlager strebt danach, die erste Wahl für Kunden im Bereich Wohn- und Schlafkomfort zu sein und arbeitet eng mit verschiedenen Partnern zusammen, um ein vielfältiges Sortiment anzubieten, das sowohl im stationären Handel als auch online verfügbar ist. Die Produktpalette reicht von Schlafzimmermöbeln bis hin zu Gartenaccessoires und spricht Kunden an, die Wert auf Qualität und ansprechendes Design legen. JYSK ist stolz auf seine skandinavischen Wurzeln und hat sich auch dem Thema Nachhaltigkeit verschrieben, indem es umweltfreundliche Materialien wie FSC-zertifiziertes Holz verwendet.  Das Unternehmen bietet zudem spezielle Rabatte und Dienstleistungen für den B2B-Bereich an, um den Bedürfnissen seiner Geschäftskunden gerecht zu werden. Durch kontinuierliche Entwicklungsmöglichkeiten für Mitarbeiter und ein starkes Engagement für Kundenzufriedenheit positioniert sich Dänisches Bettenlager als vertrauenswürdiger Anbieter in der Möbelbranche.

Name: Nanu-Nana
Company description: Nanu-Nana ist ein inhabergeführtes Familienunternehmen, das sich auf den Vertrieb von dekorativen Produkten spezialisiert hat und europaweit in Ländern wie Deutschland, Österreich, Tschechien und Polen tätig ist. Die Mission des Unternehmens ist es, ansprechende und trendige Dekoartikel anzubieten, die den Wünschen der Kunden entsprechen. Nanu-Nana legt großen Wert auf die Zufriedenheit seiner Mitarbeitenden und bietet zahlreiche Benefits, darunter flexible Arbeitszeiten, individuelle Weiterbildungsmöglichkeiten und attraktive Vergütung. Das Unternehmen richtet sich an eine breite Zielgruppe, die Wert auf stilvolle und kreative Wohnaccessoires legt, und sucht motivierte Mitarbeiter für verschiedene Positionen in den Filialen sowie in der Zentrale in Oldenburg. Durch regelmäßigen Austausch mit den Filialen und eine intensive Einarbeitung fördert Nanu-Nana eine starke Teamkultur und ein positives Arbeitsumfeld.

Name: Nolte Küchen GmbH & Co. KG
Company description: Nolte Küchen GmbH & Co. KG is a distinguished German kitchen manufacturer headquartered in Löhne, specializing in high-quality kitchen cabinetry that seamlessly blends innovative design with functionality. Established in 1958, this family-owned company has earned accolades as "Germany's favorite kitchen brand," underscoring its unwavering commitment to quality, sustainability, and customer satisfaction. Nolte Küchen's mission is to create kitchens that serve as the heart of the home, where families can gather and share experiences, emphasizing personalization and adaptability in their designs. The company caters to a diverse clientele, including homeowners, interior designers, and kitchen retailers, and collaborates with various partners to offer a wide range of customizable options. With a strong focus on sustainability, Nolte Küchen employs eco-friendly practices and materials, striving to minimize its environmental impact while delivering stylish and durable kitchen solutions tailored to individual needs and budgets. The company operates exclusively within Germany, with production facilities located in Löhne and Melle, where it prioritizes sustainably sourced materials and innovative manufacturing processes to reduce waste. Nolte Küchen aims to provide long-lasting satisfaction to its customers by ensuring the durability and reparability of its products, while also engaging in proactive dialogue with suppliers to uphold sustainability standards. Dedicated to meeting the evolving demands of consumers who prioritize eco-friendly solutions, Nolte Küchen primarily serves the kitchen retail market, collaborating with kitchen studios and furniture stores. The company is also committed to social responsibility, actively participating in community initiatives and supporting various charitable causes, reflecting its desire to make a positive impact both locally and globally. As one of the world's largest kitchen furniture manufacturers, Nolte Küchen is renowned for its quality, innovation, and sustainability, all proudly produced in Germany.

Name: Hülsta-werke Hüls GmbH & Co. KG
Company description: Hülsta-werke Hüls GmbH & Co. KG is a renowned German furniture manufacturer specializing in high-quality, stylish furniture for living, sleeping, and dining spaces. With a commitment to excellence, the company emphasizes meticulous craftsmanship, timeless design, and sustainability in its products, which are well-regarded for their durability and aesthetic appeal. Hülsta's mission is to create innovative and functional furniture solutions that enhance everyday living, while its vision focuses on expanding its product range to include comprehensive home furnishing options, such as kitchens. The company caters to a diverse clientele, including individual consumers and interior designers, and collaborates with various retail partners to deliver customized solutions that meet the unique needs of its customers. Through its ongoing dedication to quality and design, Hülsta aims to inspire and elevate the living experiences of its customers.

Name: XXXLutz Österreich
Company description: XXXLutz Österreich is a prominent furniture and home goods retailer, known for its extensive range of products that cater to various customer needs in home furnishing. The company aims to provide high-quality, stylish, and affordable solutions for creating comfortable living spaces, aligning with its mission to enhance the quality of life for its customers. XXXLutz has established a strong connection with its audience through innovative marketing campaigns, such as the recent film featuring the well-known Putz family, which showcases their journey in Hollywood, reflecting the brand's commitment to creativity and entertainment. The target market includes families and individuals looking for comprehensive home solutions, while partnerships with creative agencies and production teams help to elevate its brand presence in the competitive retail landscape. With a focus on customer satisfaction and a vision to be a leader in the home furnishing sector, XXXLutz continues to expand its influence across Austria and beyond.

Name: ELLOS GROUP
Company description: Ellos Group är en ledande nordisk shoppingdestination för heminredning och mode med onlinebutikerna Ellos, Jotex och Homeroom samt betalvarumärket Elpy. I nära relation med våra miljontals kunder utvecklar vi attraktiva och hållbara erbjudanden för kvinnan mitt i livet, hennes familj och hem. Med innovation, kreativitet och hållbarhet söker vi ständigt nya vägar i stort och smått, och alltid med kunden i fokus. Ellos Group, med huvudkontor i Borås, är verksamt i samtliga nordiska länder och på utvalda marknader i Europa. Ellos Group har ca 500 medarbetare och omsätter runt 3,3 miljarder SEK.   The Ellos Group, which includes the online stores Ellos, Jotex, Homeroom and payment brand Elpy, is a leading shopping destination for fashion and home furnishings in the Nordic region. Working closely with our millions of customers, we offer attractive and sustainable products for the woman in mid-life, her family and home. We continuously develop our business through innovation, creativity, and sustainability, and always focusing on the customer. The Ellos Group, headquartered in Borås, and with operations in all Nordic countries and selected European markets, has around 500 employees and sales of around SEK 3.3 billion.

Name: OKAY
HQ Location: Czech Republic, South Moravian, Brno, 676/259 Kšírova
Company description: Společnost OKAY začínala před více než 25 lety s prodejem elektra a po převzetí značky JENA v roce 2012 rozšířila své pole působení také o nábytek. Dnes jsme největším prodejcem elektra a nábytku v ČR s širokou sítí prodejen i v menších městech a s e-shopy okay.cz, okay.sk a jena-nabytek.cz

Name: Swedwood
Company description: Swedwood is the industrial group within IKEA. The primary function is to manufacture and distribute furniture. Swedwood “integrates backwards” in the supply chain to lower costs and efficiently distribute the products. Swedwood is open to every possible type of cost cutting, and IKEA’s motto, “Nothing is impossible”, is the guiding principle throughout our business.

Name: FOURLIS Group Of Companies
Company description: Headquartered in Athens and boasting a successful history of over 70 years, Fourlis Group is a dynamic force in the retail sector in Southeast Europe. Fourlis Group comprises leading omnichannel retail companies, dedicated to serving customers across Greece, Romania, Bulgaria and Cyprus with high quality consumer goods.  We specialize in Retail Home Furnishings, through our franchise of IKEA stores, Retail Sporting Goods, as an exclusive licensee of INTERSPORT trademark, and Foot Locker trademark, and most recently Retail Health & Wellness, through our franchise of HOLLAND & BARRETT stores. Committed to sustainable growth and value creation, Fourlis Group has also invested into the real estate sector with the establishment of TRADE ESTATES REIC, a company listed in the Athens Stock Exchange specializing in retail parks and omnichannel logistics.  Our success is rooted in our unwavering dedication to fostering strong relationships with our employees and suppliers, investing in cutting-edge infrastructure, and prioritizing customer satisfaction to deliver exceptional quality and experiences. As proud members of the United Nations Global Compact since 2008, we remain steadfast in our commitment to responsible business practices. The Group’s strategy focuses on expanding through companies specializing in retail commerce. Our entrance into growing sectors like household equipment, sporting goods, health & wellness, and real estate forms the core of our growth pillars. To achieve our goals, we remain committed to: -	Adapting to market needs and conditions. -	Expanding commercial and service areas. -	Promoting synergies within the Group and forming alliances. -	Creating efficiencies through optimizations and investing in digitalization and innovative new technologies. -	Keeping our focus on attracting, developing, and retaining talent.

Name: Staples Portugal
Company description: Staples Portugal é uma empresa especializada na venda de produtos e serviços para escritório, oferecendo uma ampla gama de materiais, equipamentos e soluções para atender às necessidades de empresas e consumidores individuais. Com uma missão voltada para facilitar o trabalho e a criatividade, a Staples se posiciona como um parceiro confiável para profissionais de diversas indústrias, desde pequenas empresas até grandes corporações. A empresa se destaca pela sua vasta seleção de produtos, que inclui desde material de escritório e tecnologia até mobiliário e artigos de papelaria. O seu público-alvo abrange tanto clientes empresariais quanto consumidores finais, buscando sempre proporcionar uma experiência de compra eficiente e acessível. Além disso, a Staples Portugal colabora com diversas marcas e fornecedores para garantir a qualidade e a inovação em seus produtos e serviços.

Name: BAUHAUS Danmark A/S
Company description: BAUHAUS Danmark A/S is a leading retailer in the home improvement and DIY sector, specializing in a wide range of products including tools, building materials, and home furnishings. The company is committed to providing high-quality products at competitive prices, aiming to enhance the shopping experience for both professional contractors and DIY enthusiasts. BAUHAUS serves a diverse clientele, including individual consumers, tradespeople, and businesses, and partners with reputable brands such as Ryobi and Bosch to offer reliable and innovative solutions. With a focus on customer satisfaction, BAUHAUS strives to deliver efficient service and quick delivery options, ensuring that customers can easily access the products they need for their projects. The company's vision is to be the go-to destination for all home improvement needs, fostering a culture of creativity and practicality in home and garden projects.

Name: ArredissimA
Company description: ArredissimA is a prominent Italian furniture company that specializes in providing tailored home furnishing solutions for various living spaces, including kitchens, living rooms, and bedrooms. The company prides itself on its commitment to quality and customer satisfaction, which is reflected in its partnership with beloved Italian television icon Gerry Scotti, who serves as a brand ambassador. ArredissimA aims to create a welcoming and engaging shopping experience, offering personalized consultations to help clients design their dream homes. With a diverse range of products that cater to both classic and modern tastes, the company targets a wide audience, from families to young professionals seeking stylish and functional furniture. Through its showrooms and online presence, ArredissimA continues to innovate and expand its offerings, ensuring that every customer finds the perfect pieces to enhance their living environment.

Name: Homefashion Group B.V.
Company description: Homefashion Group B.V. is a dynamic company specializing in home furnishings and interior design solutions, operating under well-known brands such as Leen Bakker and Kwantum. The company is committed to enhancing the customer experience through innovative omnichannel strategies, new retail concepts, and personalized home advisory services, including delivery and assembly. With a strong focus on employee development and satisfaction, Homefashion Group has recently achieved the Top Employer certification, reflecting its dedication to creating a positive work environment. The company aims to lead the market by providing sustainable and appealing commercial propositions, targeting families and individuals looking to transform their living spaces. Under the leadership of CEO Linda Keijzer, who brings extensive retail experience, Homefashion Group is poised for continued growth and success in the competitive home fashion industry.

Name: Scavolini S.p.A.
Company description: Scavolini S.p.A. is a renowned Italian company specializing in the design and manufacturing of high-quality kitchen and bathroom furniture. Established in 1961, Scavolini has built a reputation for creating innovative and stylish solutions that enhance the functionality and aesthetics of living spaces. The company's mission is to provide customers with personalized and sustainable products that reflect their unique tastes and lifestyles, ensuring that each piece is crafted with precision and care. Scavolini collaborates with a network of skilled artisans and designers, which allows it to offer a diverse range of customizable options tailored to individual preferences. Targeting both residential and commercial markets, Scavolini serves a wide clientele that includes homeowners, architects, and interior designers. The company maintains a strong presence in international markets, appealing to consumers who value quality craftsmanship and contemporary design. Scavolini's vision emphasizes leadership in design excellence and sustainability, as it continuously integrates cutting-edge technology and eco-friendly practices into its production processes. With a focus on customer satisfaction, Scavolini aims to transform everyday environments into extraordinary spaces, making it a preferred choice for those seeking elegance and practicality in their home furnishings. The brand is recognized for its commitment to quality and innovation, consistently setting trends in the furniture industry while enhancing the quality of life for its customers. Through its dedication to craftsmanship and design, Scavolini envisions a future where every home reflects the individuality and lifestyle of its inhabitants.

Name: Black Red White
Company description: Black Red White is a prominent furniture retailer based in Poland, renowned for its extensive range of home furnishings that includes living room, bedroom, and kitchen furniture, as well as decorative accessories. The company is dedicated to enhancing the comfort and aesthetics of living spaces through high-quality products, with a strong commitment to customer satisfaction and innovative design. Black Red White serves a diverse clientele, catering to individual consumers and families seeking to furnish their homes, as well as businesses in need of commercial furniture solutions.  Operating both physical showrooms and an online store, Black Red White provides customers with the convenience of browsing and purchasing products from anywhere. The company emphasizes quality and affordability, positioning itself as a leading choice for home furnishings in the Polish market. Its mission is to enhance living spaces by offering stylish, functional, and high-quality furniture solutions that cater to a variety of tastes and preferences.  In addition to individual customers, Black Red White collaborates with various partners, including manufacturers and retailers, to ensure a comprehensive selection of products that meet the needs of its target market, which encompasses homeowners, renters, and interior designers. Through its commitment to quality and innovation, Black Red White strives to create comfortable and aesthetically pleasing environments for its clients, solidifying its reputation as a trusted name in the furniture and home decor industry.

Name: Natuzzi SpA
HQ Location: Italy, Apulia, Santeramo In Colle, 47 Via Iazzitiello
Company description: Natuzzi SpA engages in the design, production and marketing of contemporary and traditional leather and fabric upholstered furniture. The company is headquartered in Santeramo In Colle, Bari and currently employs 3,205 full-time employees.  The firm designs, manufactures and sells a collection of couches, armchairs, home furniture and home accessories. The firm operates in two segments: Natuzzi brand and Softaly/Private label. The Natuzzi brand segment includes sales from the Natuzzi Italia, Natuzzi Re-vive and Natuzzi Editions product lines. The company offers a range of upholstered furniture for sale, manufactured in production facilities located in Italy and abroad (Romania, Brazil and China). Private label includes its unbranded and Softaly products, and is marketed in North America, Europe, Brazil and Asia-Pacific through a selected number of customers. Natuzzi's range of products includes a collection of sofas and armchairs with particular styles, coverings and functions, with over two million combinations.

Name: MÖBEL MARTIN
Company description: MÖBEL MARTIN is a prominent furniture retailer in Germany, offering a wide range of home furnishings and decor solutions. The company is dedicated to providing customers with high-quality products that enhance their living spaces, while also focusing on customer satisfaction and innovative shopping experiences. With multiple locations across cities such as Kaiserslautern, Mainz, and Saarbrücken, MÖBEL MARTIN caters to a diverse clientele, including families, young professionals, and interior design enthusiasts. The company actively engages with its customers through various promotions, including newsletters that offer discounts and exclusive events, such as wine tastings and exciting giveaways. MÖBEL MARTIN's mission is to inspire and support customers in creating their ideal homes, while its vision emphasizes a commitment to quality, value, and community engagement.

Name: Mobilya
Company description: Ceo- Dott. Cantone Luciano Il marchio registrato che da oltre 40 anni identifica una delle più grandi società operanti nel settore del mobile, e non solo. Mobilya non è solo sinonimo di mobili di qualità, ma anche di complementi d’arredo, elementi indispensabili per rendere ancora più accogliente la tua casa. Il punto di forza di Mobilya è proprio l’offerta che mette a Tua disposizione. La selezione dei migliori produttori locali e nazionali Ti assicura la possibilità di trovare la soluzione di arredamento più vantaggiosa per arredare la casa. Cucine classiche e moderne, Sale da pranzo, Camere da letto, Pareti componibili, Armadi, Credenze, Camerette, un mondo di divani, divaniletto e salotti e tante soluzioni personalizzate per gli angoli relax della Tua casa: questo è il mondo Mobilya. La missione di Mobilya è “essere il mobilificio punto di riferimento per le famiglie del Centro e Sud Italia”. L’Azienda si propone di raggiungere i suoi obiettivi attraverso una costante attenzione alle esigenze del cliente, per soddisfarlo e fornirgli il miglior servizio possibile, ed uno sguardo attento al mercato, per essere sempre al passo con i tempi. E’ per questi motivi che i valori che ispirano l’operato di Mobilya e la guidano verso il raggiungimento della mission aziendale sono capisaldi condivisi da tutta l’organizzazione: costante ricerca della qualità, dinamicità e ricerca, basate sulla conoscenza ed il rispetto di tutte le esigenze.

Name: BOLIA
Company description: BOLIA is a contemporary furniture design company that specializes in creating tailor-made furniture solutions, allowing customers to customize their pieces in terms of model, size, upholstery fabric, and materials. With a strong commitment to sustainability, BOLIA aims to inspire positive change through responsible design practices, emphasizing longevity and circularity in its products. The company serves a diverse clientele, including individuals seeking stylish and functional home furnishings, and collaborates with various partners to promote responsible practices within the industry. BOLIA's target market includes design-conscious consumers who value quality, craftsmanship, and the ability to personalize their living spaces. Through its innovative approach and transparency in sustainability efforts, BOLIA strives to lead the furniture industry towards a more sustainable future.

Name: Möbel Rieger GmbH & Co. KG
Company description: Möbel Rieger GmbH & Co. KG ist ein traditionsreiches, familiengeführtes Möbelhaus, das seit 75 Jahren für Qualität, Leidenschaft und außergewöhnliche Einkaufserlebnisse steht. Das Unternehmen bietet eine breite Palette an Möbeln, Lampen, Haushaltswaren, Küchen, Heimtextilien und Dekorationen an, um den individuellen Wohnträumen seiner Kunden gerecht zu werden. Mit einem klaren Fokus auf Kundenzufriedenheit und einem engagierten Team von über 1.400 Mitarbeitern setzt Möbel Rieger alles daran, seinen Kunden ein angenehmes und inspirierendes Einkaufserlebnis zu bieten.  Das Unternehmen arbeitet eng mit verschiedenen Partnern zusammen und richtet sich an eine breite Zielgruppe, die Wert auf stilvolle und funktionale Einrichtung legt. Möbel Rieger engagiert sich aktiv in sozialen Projekten und fördert lokale Initiativen, was Teil ihrer Unternehmensphilosophie ist. Als innovatives Unternehmen im Bereich Möbel und Inneneinrichtung spezialisiert sich Möbel Rieger auf die Gestaltung und den Verkauf von hochwertigen Möbeln und Wohnaccessoires.  Mit einer klaren Mission, individuelle Wohnkonzepte zu schaffen, bietet das Unternehmen seinen Kunden eine breite Palette an Produkten, die verschiedene Einrichtungsstile wie Industrial, Boho und Vintage kombinieren. Möbel Rieger legt großen Wert auf persönliche Beratung und bietet an mehreren Standorten in Baden-Württemberg individuelle Einrichtungsberatung an, um den Kunden bei der Verwirklichung ihrer Wohnträume zu unterstützen. Die Zielgruppe umfasst sowohl private Endverbraucher als auch kreative Freigeister, die Wert auf stilvolle und funktionale Einrichtung legen. Durch die enge Zusammenarbeit mit verschiedenen Partnern und Lieferanten stellt Möbel Rieger sicher, dass die angebotenen Produkte sowohl ästhetisch ansprechend als auch von hoher Qualität sind.

Name: Titus Group
Company description: The world’s best engineering for precision components. Business activities - Titus Furniture hardware: development, manufacturing and sales of furniture connectors, concealed hinges and furniture damping. - Titus Precision components: development, manufacturing and sales of hydraulic dampers for home and commercial applications. - Titus Technologies: development, manufacturing and sales of automated assembly systems, tools and die-casting technologies. The Titus Group, with the headquarters in the UK, comprises 22 companies. It assures a global reach from several strategic manufacturing or trade locations in Europe, Asia and America: in UK, Slovenia, Poland, Croatia, USA, Mexico, Singapore, Indonesia, Australia and China.

Name: Boltze Gruppe
Company description: Die Boltze Gruppe ist ein führender Großhändler für hochwertige Wohnaccessoires und Geschenkartikel, der seit 1964 Tradition mit Innovation verbindet. Mit einem umfangreichen Sortiment von über 15.000 Artikeln bedient das Unternehmen mehr als 15.000 Kunden weltweit, darunter Möbelhändler, Baumärkte, Gartencenter und E-Commerce-Plattformen. Die Mission von Boltze ist es, durch qualitativ hochwertige Produkte und persönlichen Service den Bedürfnissen ihrer B2B-Kunden gerecht zu werden und ihnen zu helfen, ihre Kunden mit einzigartigen Dekorationsideen zu begeistern. Das Unternehmen legt großen Wert auf Zuverlässigkeit und kontinuierliche Weiterentwicklung, um stets aktuelle Trends und saisonale Highlights anzubieten.  Boltze Gruppe ist ein familiengeführtes Unternehmen, das sich auf Wohnaccessoires und Geschenkartikel spezialisiert hat und in Europa zu den führenden Anbietern zählt. Mit fast 60 Jahren Erfahrung bietet Boltze über 15.000 Produkte an, die von Kerzen und Vasen bis hin zu Außendekorationen und saisonalen Artikeln reichen. Die Unternehmensvision ist es, außergewöhnliche Qualität und Service zu bieten, während Tradition und Innovation miteinander verbunden werden, um sicherzustellen, dass ihre vielfältige Klientel Zugang zu einzigartigen und trendbewussten Produkten hat.  Boltze ist bestrebt, agil im digitalen Zeitalter zu sein und sich kontinuierlich an die Marktanforderungen anzupassen, wobei der Fokus auf Kundenzufriedenheit und einer niedrigen Beschwerdequote von unter einem Prozent liegt. Ihr umfangreiches Produktsortiment, das jährlich rund 6.000 neue Artikel umfasst, spiegelt ihr Engagement wider, den Trends voraus zu sein und die Bedürfnisse ihrer Partner und Kunden zu erfüllen. Mit einem digitalen Händlerportal und innovativen Showroom-Erlebnissen ermöglicht Boltze seinen Partnern, bequem und effizient einzukaufen und sich inspirieren zu lassen.

Name: Bohus AS
Company description: Bohus AS is a prominent Norwegian furniture retailer specializing in a wide range of home furnishings, including storage solutions, dining tables, and sofas. The company is dedicated to providing stylish and functional furniture that enhances the living spaces of its customers. With a focus on quality and affordability, Bohus aims to make beautiful home decor accessible to everyone. Its product offerings include various collections, such as the Raffels series, which features elegant storage units and dining furniture. Bohus serves a diverse clientele, including families and individuals looking to create inviting and comfortable homes, and collaborates with various suppliers to ensure a broad selection of contemporary designs. The company's mission is to inspire customers to find the perfect pieces that reflect their personal style while maintaining a commitment to value and customer satisfaction.

Name: BORNE Furniture
Company description: BORNE Furniture Sp. z o.o. is part of the German family company KMBT GmbH & Co. KG based in Trierweiler, which has been known in Western Europe for over 60 years as a producer of the latest generation of doors and door frames. In the Polish market, the history of BORNE Furniture begins in Barlinek in 1998, initially under the name Klaus Borne Door Factory. Since starting a long-term cooperation with the Swedish company Ikea in 2000, the company has been developing dynamically. Currently, the production facilities consist of two highly specialized plants located in Gorzów Wielkopolski and Barlinek, with a total production area of 37,000 m². BORNE Furniture specializes in large-scale production based on lightweight cellular board, including table tops, shelves, and other furniture components. The company employs around 800 people and is a respected employer in the region. The atmosphere and commitment of our employees allow for exceptional flexibility, dynamics, and innovative capabilities focused on the needs of our customers.

Name: Woonexpress
Company description: Woonexpress is a dynamic home furnishings company that specializes in providing a wide range of stylish and comfortable furniture and home accessories. With a mission to enhance living spaces, Woonexpress aims to make quality interior design accessible to everyone, offering products that cater to various tastes and preferences. The company operates nine physical stores across the Netherlands, ensuring that customers can easily find and purchase their desired items, while also providing an online shopping experience with exclusive web-only collections. Woonexpress prides itself on excellent customer service, reflected in its high customer ratings, and offers flexible payment options, including direct payment, deferred payment, or installment plans. The target market includes individuals and families looking to refresh their homes with trendy and functional decor, and the company collaborates with popular media programs to showcase its products, further enhancing its visibility and appeal.

Name: Zurbrüggen Wohn-Zentrum GmbH
Company description: Zurbrüggen Wohn-Zentrum GmbH is a prominent furniture retailer in Germany, specializing in a wide range of home furnishings, including kitchenware, living room furniture, and decorative items. The company aims to provide high-quality products at competitive prices, making stylish living accessible to a broad audience. With a focus on customer satisfaction, Zurbrüggen offers personalized consultation services and various promotions, such as significant discounts during special shopping events. Their target market includes families and individuals looking to furnish their homes with modern and affordable solutions. The company collaborates with well-known brands and manufacturers to ensure a diverse selection of products that meet contemporary design trends.

Name: Johannes Fog A/S
Company description: Velkommen i Fog Hos os får du kvalificeret rådgivning til den bedste løsning. Vi hjælper dig med at få overblik og komme i mål med dit byggeprojekt. Lige fra hvad der er godt at vide til vejledning i valg af materialer. Fog består af et Bolig & Designhus og ni Trælast & Byggecenter-butikker fordelt i hele Nordsjælland – i Hørsholm, Fredensborg, Kvistgård, Helsinge, Lyngby, Ølstykke, Herlev og Farum. Vi har også en butik mere sydpå i Vordingborg, der også har stor ekspertise i salg af jern, stål og andre metaller. I trælasten har vi træ og byggematerialer til alle slags opgaver. Vi har et stort udvalg, hvor du kan vælge mellem mange muligheder, både hvad angår størrelser og kvaliteter. Byggecentrene har alt til hjemmet inden for bl.a. værktøj, maling, bad, beslag, el, lamper og pejseartikler. Vi kan hjælpe dig med valget af f.eks. en ny græsslåmaskine. Der er power til forskel, men det handler om at vælge værktøjet til lige præcis dit behov. Ordentlige haveredskaber og -møbler kan holde i rigtig mange år. Hos os får du kvalitet. Her er der forskellige slags havemøbler at vælge i mellem, parasoller der bare holder, terrassevarmere og meget andet, der bidrager til det hyggelige udeliv. Få kompetent rådgivning i Fog, så du nemt kan vælge. Fog på Nørgaardsvej i Lyngby er helt speciel. Det er vores Bolig & Designhus. Her finder du udover de traditionelle byggecenter-varer også lækkert design og idéer til boligen indenfor køkken- og badudstyr, farve og tapeter, garderober, solafskærmning, stort udvalg af havemøbler og Nordens største lampeafdeling med alle de kendte designlamper.

Name: Rutar Group
Company description: Rutar Group is a prominent player in the home furnishings and interior design sector, dedicated to transforming living spaces into personalized sanctuaries. With a mission to inspire and enhance the everyday lives of its customers, Rutar offers a diverse range of products, including stylish furniture, innovative kitchen designs, and artistic home decor. The company prides itself on its commitment to quality and authenticity, ensuring that each piece resonates with the beauty of everyday life. Rutar serves a wide clientele, from individual homeowners seeking to create their dream spaces to businesses looking for functional and aesthetic solutions. Collaborating with renowned brands like Interliving, Stressless®, and Voglauer, Rutar aims to redefine comfort and style in home living.  With over 65 years of experience, Rutar continues to be a trusted partner in realizing residential dreams, fostering a deep connection between people and their homes. The company specializes in high-quality furniture and accessories for various living spaces, offering a wide range of services, including furniture delivery, assembly, and financing options, ensuring a seamless shopping experience for its customers. Rutar's clientele includes families and individuals seeking stylish and functional home furnishings, while its partnerships with leading brands enhance its product offerings. Committed to customer satisfaction, Rutar emphasizes quality, affordability, and innovative design, making it a trusted choice for home decor enthusiasts. Through its dedication to creating inviting and personalized environments, Rutar Group transforms houses into homes that reflect individual tastes and lifestyles.

Name: Einrichtungshaus Föger
Company description: Einrichtungshaus Föger is a prominent furniture store located in Tirol, known for its extensive selection of high-quality furniture and home decor. The company prides itself on being "the largest small furniture house" in the region, offering a diverse range of products to meet the needs of its clients. Föger's mission is to create a welcoming shopping experience that transforms houses into homes, emphasizing comfort and style. The store actively engages with its community through initiatives like weekly giveaways, encouraging customer interaction via social media platforms such as Facebook and Instagram. Its target market includes local residents in Austria who are looking for unique and stylish furnishings, while also fostering partnerships with various suppliers to ensure a wide array of choices for its customers.

Name: SCONTO Nábytek S.r.o.
Company description: SCONTO Nábytek s.r.o. je součástí německého koncernu Höffner, který patří k největším prodejcům nábytku v Evropě. Najdete u nás kompletní sortiment bytového nábytku, který zahrnuje obývací stěny, sedací soupravy, pohovky, konferenční stolky, ložnice, matrace, rošty, dětské pokoje, kuchyně, jídelny, židle, stoly, kancelářský a koupelnový nábytek, svítidla, bytový textil a další kuchyňské i bytové doplňky.

Name: MERKAMUEBLE
Company description: Merkamueble is a dynamic online furniture retailer specializing in a wide range of home furnishings, including living room, bedroom, and juvenile furniture, as well as mattresses and decorative items. The company's mission is to enhance the shopping experience by offering high-quality products at competitive prices, with promotions such as discounts of up to 60% and flexible payment options. Merkamueble caters to a diverse clientele, including families, young adults, and gamers, providing tailored solutions for various living spaces. The company partners with reputable manufacturers to ensure a broad selection of stylish and functional furniture that meets the needs of its customers. With a focus on customer satisfaction and convenience, Merkamueble aims to be a leading choice for those looking to furnish their homes with modern and affordable options.

Name: Hjort Knudsen A/S
Company description: HJORT KNUDSEN A/S Hjort Knudsen is one of the biggest suppliers of  upholstered furniture for furniture stores in Sweden, Denmark and Norway, with sales offices in all three countries. Hjort Knudsen is also sold in the Netherlands and Germany. The company has an extensive range of both chairs and sofas, which can be combined.The product range spans the traditional to the contemporary, and all products are available in both fabric and leather. In addition to upholstered furniture, Hjort Knudsen also makes wooden furniture. Goal: It is our goal to always create the best furniture in a design in tune with the times and with optimum seating comfort. Our guideline is value for money. Hjort Knudsen takes full responsibility for the entire furniture manufacturing process.We create our own designs and our products are manufactured in our own factories, where we test functionality and seating comfort. Our factories in Europe, which have over 2,000 employees, are 100% owned by Hjort Knudsen.The company also has its own distribution department, with 52  lorries with 117m3cargo capacity, to ensure fast, effective store deliveries. About Hjort Knudsen A/S Hjort Knudsen A/S is a Danish family-owned furniture manufacturer, founded in 1973 by Ina and Arne Hjort Knudsen. Since 2000 the company’s ownership and management has been in the hands of the next generation of Ellen and Klaus Hjort Knudsen. The head office is based in West Jutland.

Name: Möbelix
Company description: Jsme Möbelix, síť prodejen nábytku a bytových doplňků. Patříme k rakouskému koncernu XXXLutz a v současné době rosteme nejrychleji ze všech obchodních sítí v Evropě. V Čechách a na Slovensku nás najdete 18x, od Karlových Varů až po Košice.  Znáte Möbelix? Zamyslete se znovu. Möbelix je na českém a slovenském trhu 11 let a  během posledních 3 let prošel radikální změnou. Z diskontních prodejen se staly reprezentativní obchodní domy, kde si přijdou na své především zákazníci, kteří chtějí moderně a prakticky bydlet. Moderní nábytek pro moderní zákazníky. To je naše vize. Sortiment vybíráme tak, abychom zákazníkům dávali nový impuls a neúnavně je inspirovali aktuálními trendy. Kromě atraktivního nábytku nabízíme perfektní servis, mimo jiné 3D plánování s tabletem na prodejně nebo digitální záměr kuchyně u zákazníka s přenosem dat. Zákazníkovi nabízíme zážitek, emoci a nikdy nezapomínáme na lidský přístup.  A to nejen  ve vztahu k zákazníkům ale především k našim zaměstnancům. Ctíme férovost a kolegialitu.

Name: Centro Veneto Del Mobile
HQ Location: Italy, San, 22 Via Giuseppe Di Vittorio, 30029
Company description: Centro Veneto del Mobile is a leading provider of high-quality furniture solutions in Italy, dedicated to delivering a seamless shopping experience from consultation to delivery. The company prides itself on its meticulous attention to detail, ensuring that every piece of furniture is carefully transported and assembled by skilled artisans. With a mission to enhance customer satisfaction, Centro Veneto del Mobile offers personalized financing options in collaboration with Findomestic Spa, making stylish home furnishings accessible to a wider audience. Their commitment to quality is underscored by an extended warranty of up to seven years on kitchen designs, reflecting their focus on durability and customer peace of mind. Serving a diverse clientele across Italy, the company emphasizes a stress-free delivery process and responsive post-sale support, ensuring that every customer feels valued and supported throughout their purchasing journey.

Name: VICKO
Company description: VICKO | Τρόπος για να ζεις. Από το 1978, η VICKO αποτελεί σημείο αναφοράς στον τομέα των ειδών σπιτιού, προσφέροντας προϊόντα που συνδυάζουν ποιότητα, σύγχρονο σχεδιασμό και προσιτές τιμές. Με περισσότερα από 180 καταστήματα και συνεργαζόμενα σημεία πώλησης σε Ελλάδα, Κύπρο και Βαλκάνια, η VICKO διαθέτει πάνω από 1.500 προϊόντα που καλύπτουν κάθε ανάγκη του σπιτιού: είδη κουζίνας, αξεσουάρ οργάνωσης, ηλεκτρικές οικιακές συσκευές, είδη μπάνιου, διακοσμητικά, έπιπλα και λευκά είδη. Η διαρκής ανανέωση της συλλογής μας, η έμφαση στη λειτουργικότητα και η δέσμευσή μας στην υψηλή αξία σε κάθε αγορά, μας καθιστούν μια από τις πιο σταθερές επιλογές του σύγχρονου καταναλωτή. Στη VICKO, πιστεύουμε ότι το σπίτι είναι κάτι περισσότερο από ένας χώρος: είναι ο τρόπος που ζεις.

Name: Home Center
Company description: Home Center is a premier retail destination specializing in high-quality home furnishings and interior design solutions. With a mission to create stylish and functional living spaces, the company partners with renowned brands like Area77 to offer a diverse range of innovative products, including cinewalls, TV furniture, and custom-made pieces. Home Center caters to a wide array of clients, from homeowners seeking to enhance their living environments to interior designers looking for unique and sustainable materials. The company is committed to delivering exceptional craftsmanship and personalized service, ensuring that every customer finds the perfect fit for their individual style and needs. With a focus on quality and detail, Home Center aims to be the go-to source for those looking to transform their homes into beautiful and organized spaces.

Name: Office Depot Sweden
Company description: Vi är kontorets one-stop-shop. Hos oss kan du handla allt till kontoret från samma leverantör. Färre fakturor, transporter och leveranser, för att spara på tid och miljö. Utöver ett omfattande sortiment av allt tänkbart kontorsmaterial erbjuder vi även möbler, kaffemaskiner, konferensutrustning och skrivarlösningar till kunder över hela landet. Genom våra 41 butiker, e-handel och en rikstäckande säljkår finns vi alltid nära tillhands när det behövs något till kontoret. Vi finns helt enkelt till för att göra ditt arbetsliv lite enklare. Office Depot har utsetts till en av de 100 mest spännande arbetsgivarna i Sverige, och det är inte utan anledning! Med modern företagskultur jobbar vi ständigt för en utvecklande arbetsplats som engagerar våra medarbetare. På Office Depot vet vi att det är vi som jobbar här som gör skillnaden. Varumärket Office Depot grundades 1986 i USA och finns idag i mer än 50 länder. Office Depot Svenska AB omsätter drygt 1 miljard och har cirka 350 medarbetare.

Name: Juskys Gruppe GmbH
Company description: Juskys Gruppe GmbH is a dynamic company based in Holle, Niedersachsen, specializing in a diverse range of products that include furniture, garden supplies, leisure items, household goods, and pet accessories. The company is dedicated to providing high-quality products at competitive prices, ensuring customer satisfaction through excellent service and a user-friendly shopping experience. Juskys targets a broad market, catering to families, pet owners, and individuals looking to enhance their living spaces and outdoor environments. With a focus on convenience, they offer free shipping within Germany and a hassle-free return policy, making it easy for customers to shop confidently.  The company values its community of over 200,000 satisfied customers and continuously strives to meet their needs and preferences. Juskys Gruppe GmbH is committed to the online sale of furniture, garden items, and leisure products, with a wide product range that includes high-quality children's furniture, garden furniture, and fitness equipment. The mission of Juskys is to offer quality products at fair prices, while their vision is to become a leading provider in the e-commerce sector for furniture and leisure items. Their target audience includes families, gardening enthusiasts, and fitness lovers who prioritize safety, comfort, and appealing design. Juskys collaborates closely with various partners to ensure fast delivery and excellent customer service, contributing to high levels of customer satisfaction.

Name: FDB
Company description: FDB Møbler is a Danish furniture company renowned for its commitment to high-quality, handcrafted pieces that blend traditional craftsmanship with modern design aesthetics. The company’s mission is to create functional and timeless furniture that enhances everyday living, while its vision focuses on celebrating Danish design heritage through innovative and sustainable practices. FDB Møbler collaborates with talented designers, such as Laura Bilde, to produce a diverse range of products, including sofas, chairs, and tables, that cater to both residential and hospitality markets. The company targets design-conscious consumers who appreciate the beauty of natural materials and the importance of durability in their furniture choices. With a strong emphasis on quality and comfort, FDB Møbler aims to be a central part of its customers' homes, providing pieces that evoke a sense of warmth and style.

Name: Ikano Industry Polska
HQ Location: Poland, Greater Poland, Rogoźno, 4 Ul. Magazynowa, 64-610
Company description: Ikano Industry to firma wchodząca w skład międzynarodowej grupy kapitałowej, jeden z czołowych producentów materaców piankowych dla sieci sklepów IKEA.  Jesteśmy jedną z największych i najnowocześniejszych fabryk produkujących materace piankowe w Europie. Ikano Industry is a part of an international group and one of the leading manufacturers of foam mattresses for the IKEA chain of stores. We are one of the largest and most modern factories producing foam mattresses in Europe.

Name: Industrial Laborum Ibérica
Company description: EN Industrial Laborum Ibérica, S.A. was established in 1978, as the first Portuguese company to manufacture and install laboratory furniture. Since then, it became specialized in the design, planning, marketing, manufacturing, distribution and installation of laboratory furniture and equipment, becoming an essential reference in the market. Industrial Laborum Ibérica's vision complies innovation, functionality and design of the equipment and, therefore, it develops integrated solutions completely appropriate to the quality and safety requirements of its customers. PT A Industrial Laborum Ibérica, S.A. foi fundada em 1978, como a primeira empresa portuguesa a produzir e instalar mobiliário de laboratório. Desde então, dedica-se ao planeamento, projeto, fabrico, comercialização e instalação de mobiliário e equipamento de laboratório, tornando-se uma referência incontornável. Tendo como visão a inovação, design e a funcionalidade dos equipamentos, a Industrial Laborum Ibérica desenvolve soluções integradas adequadas aos requisitos de Qualidade e Segurança dos seus Clientes. FR Industrial Laborum Ibérica, S.A. a été fondée em 1978, comme la première société portugaise à produire et installer du mobilier de laboratoire. Depuis lors s'est consacrée à la planification, au projet, à la fabrication, à la commercialisation et à l'installation de mobilier de laboratoire, se transformant en une référence incontournable. Ayant comme vision l'innovation, le design et la fonctionnalité des équipements, Industrial Laborum Ibérica développe des solutions intégrées et appropriées aux exigences de Qualité et Securité de ses clients.

Name: Semeraro
Company description: Siamo italiani, amiamo l’arredamento, siamo passionali, creativi con la forza di credere nelle nostre idee e con la voglia di realizzarle. La nostra tradizione è italiana legata all’arredamento, alla moda, alla cucina, al cibo, al vino all’arte del saper vivere felicemente, qualità che ci distingue nel mondo. Sviluppiamo e proponiamo arredamenti e oggetti per la casa garantendo impegno nella ricerca dei materiali in forme e colori per rendere il tuo ambiente piacevole ed accogliente. Amiamo tutto ciò che facciamo e, ogni giorno sviluppiamo oggetti di arredamento in uno stile nel quale ci riconosciamo; il gusto che nasce dalla tradizione italiana. Il nostro sviluppo creativo è in continua evoluzione con sensibilità, cultura, condivisione e conoscenza. Il nostro obiettivo è garantire ai nostri clienti valori che corrispondono a qualità, onestà e trasparenza. Ci impegniamo per la soddisfazione dei nostri clienti. Farti vivere la tua casa con funzionalità e soddisfazione è la nostra missione. Ti promettiamo il rispetto dell’ambiente che ti circonda avendone cura al fine di avere un rapporto di trasparenza in quanto sicuri di considerarti tra i nostri nuovi messaggeri.

Name: Conforteam - Sofas & Mattresses
Company description: For nearly 20 years, we have been designing and manufacturing sofas, benches, armchairs, mattresses and other upholstered items for home furnishings in our factories.

Name: Domóvel - The Largest European Furniture Shopping Center
HQ Location: Portugal, Carvalhosa Paços De, Rua São Domingos, 4590-073
Company description: Domóvel in Paços de Ferreira was built in 2000 in order to provide an effective and varied response to the most basic and elementary needs of furniture and decoration. And so was born one of the largest furniture shopping centers, with 115 stores in 3 buildings - about 30,000 m2 of exhibition area. With a bold architecture, these 3 buildings have amazing stores managed by a substantial number of the largest furniture manufacturers and traders in the region. Being Paços de Ferreira the "Capital of Furniture", recognized nationally and internationally by the number of companies related to this sector and the quality and excellence of its furniture products, Domóvel Shopping Center became one of the greatest symbols of this land. ----- A 3 de Junho de 2000 é inaugurado o Centro Comercial Domóvel em Paços de Ferreira, com o objectivo de dar uma resposta eficaz e variada às necessidades mais básicas e elementares de mobiliário e decoração para o lar. Nasceu assim um dos maiores centros comerciais de móveis do mundo, com 115 lojas distribuídas por 3 edifícios, o que perfaz cerca de 30.000 m2 de área de exposição. Com uma arquitectura arrojada, estes 3 edifícios albergam uma quantidade substancial dos maiores fabricantes e comerciantes de móveis da região. Sendo Paços de Ferreira a "Capital do Móvel", reconhecida nacional e internacionalmente pela quantidade de empresas ligadas a este sector e pela qualidade e excelência dos seus produtos de mobiliário, o Centro Comercial Domóvel tornou-se num dos maiores símbolos do Norte de Portugal. Todo um conjunto de factores ligados a estes que referimos faz com que a solução para o que procura esteja, sem dúvida alguma, no Centro Comercial Domóvel.

Name: PROVOST Polska
Company description: Polski Producent systemów regałowych od 1963 roku, PROVOST jest jeden z leaderów w sektorze wyposażenia firm, Regały, Antresole, pomosty, zabudowy systemowe oraz szereg rozwiązań do wyposażenia magazynów i zakładów produkcyjnych (warsztaty, biura, powierzchnie handlowe itp.)   Provost oferuje 6 gam produktów, które spełnią wszystkie Twoje potrzeby związane z wyposażeniem Twojego magazynu, zakładu, warsztatu, lub sklepu : - Regały: półkowe, paletowe, wspornikowe, wielopoziomowe zabudowy i sklepowe - Zagospodarowanie przestrzeni: Antresole i pomosty, Systemowe rozbieralne ściany przemysłowe i biurowe - Plastikowe pojemniki i kuwety magazynowe - Wózki i kontenery stalowe : Ręczne magazynowe, sztaplowane palety i kontenery - Stoły i meble metalowe : Stoły do pakowania, warsztatowe, szafy ubraniowe  - Składowanie substancji niebezpiecznych : wanny wychwytowe Nasi doradca znajdują się w całym kraju blisko ciebie i pomogą ci wybrać najkorzystniejszego rozwiązania PROVOST .

Name: Pacyga Meble
HQ Location: Poland, Lesser Poland Voivodeship, Krzeszów, 86a Kuków, 34-206
Company description: Historia firmy Pacyga sięga roku 1991, kiedy to w miejscowości Lachowice, w niewielkim przydomowym garażu właściciele firmy Halina i Krzysztof Pacyga, rozpoczęli produkcję szachów. Niezwykle ważnym dla rozwoju firmy krokiem, była podjęta w 1993 roku decyzja o współpracy z firmą IKEA. W roku 1996 w miejscowości Kuków powstała nowa fabryka. Jej powierzchnia i wyposażenie pozwoliło sprostać coraz większym zamówieniom. Przez kolejne lata stale inwestowaliśmy w przestrzeń produkcyjną, która jest w stanowi pomieścić niezbędne urządzenia oraz większą ilość osób potrzebnych do pracy. I tak ze 180 m2 doszliśmy na dzień dzisiejszy do 11 500 m2 powierzchni produkcyjnej. W naszej ofercie posiadamy bogaty wybór mebli dziecięcych i młodzieżowych. Specjalizujemy się w produkcji łóżeczek dla dzieci. Produkujemy kompletne zestawy mebli poczynając od łóżeczek dla mniejszych i większych dzieci, jak i krzesełka, komody i regały, a także inne komponenty. Nie spoczywamy na laurach, szukamy nowych horyzontów do działania – wszystko z myślą o Kliencie, którego zadowolenie jest dla nas najwyższym priorytetem!

Name: ILCAM Group
HQ Location: Italy, Gorizia, Cormons, 9 Via A. Volta, 34071
Company description: Da oltre 60 anni siamo il principale produttore di componenti per l’industria del mobile.  Ci rivolgiamo ai produttori di arredamento, ai distributori di componenti, ai rivenditori e alle aziende che operano nell’ambito delle forniture contract.  Nel tempo abbiamo conquistato la fiducia dei mercati internazionali attraverso un lavoro fondato sulla condivisione, sull’attitudine a fare squadra e sulla capacità di costruire un rapporto speciale con i clienti.  Sotto il cappello ILCAM Group la competenza di sei aziende, ciascuna specializzata in diverse lavorazioni.

Name: Foppapedretti Spa
HQ Location: Italy, Bg, Grumello Del Monte, 11 Via Alessandro Volta, 24064
Company description: Foppapedretti Spa is a renowned Italian company specializing in high-quality textile products for children, including bedding sets, mattresses, and furniture. With a mission to create essential and tender items that enhance the comfort and safety of children's spaces, the company emphasizes the use of premium materials such as 100% cotton and polyester. Foppapedretti's product lines, like the Birbante and My Little Love collections, are designed to appeal to parents who value both functionality and aesthetic charm in their children's rooms. The company partners with retailers to distribute its products, targeting families looking for reliable and stylish solutions for their children's needs. Committed to quality and customer satisfaction, Foppapedretti Spa aims to be a trusted name in the realm of children's home furnishings.

Name: Ecolor
Company description: Ecolor este o echipă de peste 650 de colegi care fac mai frumoase casele a milioane de oameni din întreaga lume. Rezultatele muncii noastre se văd, zi de zi, în magazinele IKEA. Compania-mamă a Ecolor este Gyllensvaans Möbler din Suedia, producător de mobilier din 1946 și furnizor IKEA începând din 1952. De la înființarea Ecolor în România, în anul 2005, și până astăzi, activitatea și echipa fabricii au crescut constant. Această tendință continuă și azi, prin ample proiecte de investiții și prin oportunități de angajare deschise oricărui om muncitor care își dorește să fie respectat, să se simtă la serviciu ca în familie și să își construiască o carieră în industria mobilei. Întrebări despre Ecolor? Suntem aici: ne puteți contacta la info@ecolor.ro sau la numărul de telefon 0372.660.600!

Name: Sinnerup
Company description: Livsstil, kvalitet og design. Det er hjertet i Sinnerup og har været det siden Poul Sinnerup åbnede sin første butik i Holstebro i 1971.  Selvom det er længe siden de første forventningsfulde kunder trådte ind i butikken, er konceptet det samme som dengang.  Vi vil præsentere dig for det ypperste indenfor livsstil og boligindretning. Vi vil være din inspirerende samarbejdspartner.  Du skal komme ned til os når du savner inspiration, er på udkig - eller bare gerne vil hyggesnakke om tidens trends. Vi har altid tid til dig.

Name: Antarte
Company description: Antarte is a dynamic Portuguese furniture brand dedicated to reinterpreting contemporary design through innovative collections. With a mission to create spaces that reflect the lifestyle of their inhabitants, Antarte has recently launched the Dallas collection, which features over 40 pieces for dining, living, and bedroom spaces, emphasizing simplicity, functionality, and captivating shapes. The company also offers the Oslo and Malmo collections, inspired by minimalist and Scandinavian design, showcasing their commitment to modern aesthetics. Antarte's products are available through their online store and 14 retail locations across Portugal, including major cities like Lisbon and Porto. Under the leadership of CEO Mário Rocha, Antarte aims to align its offerings with market preferences, making it a go-to choice for clients seeking stylish and comfortable home furnishings.

Name: Senab Eikeland
Company description: Det starter med deg. Hos Senab Eikeland handler alt vi gjør om hva du trenger for at rommet skal fungere. Et kontor som skaper flyt i arbeidsdagen. Et klasserom der både lærer og elev finner ro. Et møterom som inviterer til gode samtaler. Vi tar oss tid til å forstå hva du vil oppnå - og hva som skal til for å komme dit. Sammen finner vi løsninger som passer til både rommet, menneskene og fremtiden. Noen ganger betyr det nye møbler. Andre ganger handler det om å se verdien i det du allerede har. Vi tilbyr rådgivning, interiørløsninger, møbelkartlegging og sirkulære tjenester. Med RE-konseptet gir vi møbler nytt liv – og hjelper deg med å ta valg som både er bærekraftige og smarte. Vår jobb er å gjøre det lett for deg å velge løsninger som varer. Og det gjør vi - hver dag - med ekte engasjement og høy fagkunnskap.

Name: Maroco
HQ Location: Portugal, Carvalhosa Paços De Ferreira, 394 Rua Da Boavista, 4590-028
Company description: Fundada em 2000, a Maroco é uma empresa sediada em Paços de Ferreira, cuja atividade consiste na comercialização de produtos para a indústria dos estofos e mobiliário. A Maroco afirmou-se no mercado com produtos de qualidade a preços competitivos, o que lhe permitiu solidificar a sua presença junto dos fabricantes de estofos através de parcerias de valor acrescentado, assim como desenvolver o seu negócio de uma forma sustentável. O portefólio da Maroco passa por ferragens, tecidos, microfibras, sintéticos, PU e semi PU, fibras, conforel, espumas, precintas elásticas, artigos de embalagem, agrafos, fios de linha, mecanismos de relax e sistemas de som.

Name: ANDI
Company description: Selle aja jooksul, alates aastast 2002, oleme valmistanud üle 6000 köögimööbli komplekti, mis on valminud algusest lõpuni meie enda poolt. Kliendid saavad meid usaldada, sest nendega koos koostame köögist 3D plaani ning kogu mööbel valmib siinsamas Eestis asuvas kaasaegse tehnoloogiaga tehases. Peale selle paigaldab mööbli seesama meister, kes selle tehases valmis teeb. Nii saame olla kindlad oma köökide kvaliteedis ja vastupidavuses.

Name: Pereda
Company description: Saneamientos Pereda Fundada en 1953 para ofrecer los mejores precios en el suministro de materiales de fontanería, con el paso de los años nos hemos convertido en la empresa líder en ventas de material de calefacción, tuberías, riego y equipamiento de baños y cocinas en la Comunidad de Madrid. Contamos con más de 12000 metros de exposición repartidos entre nuestros tres centros, que permiten a nuestros clientes elegir una amplia gama de productos de las mejores marcas. Nuestra dilatada experiencia en el sector hace de nuestro asesoramiento personalizado nuestra seña de identidad. Ofreciendo a nuestros clientes líneas sencillas, clásicas y vanguardistas, en griferías, mobiliario de baño y cocina, sanitarios, azulejos … En la sección de fontanería ofrecemos todo tipo de tubería de conducción de agua, calefacción, material de riego y jardín, productos de piscina, tratamientos de agua, placas solares y un amplio surtido de repuestos.

Name: IKEA HOUSE MARKET
Company description: We have one common vision at IKEA: to help our customers enjoy a better everyday life at home. We take our vision very seriously.  We all choose to work at IKEA because we share the unique company culture and values. We are passionate about our business and strive for high performance. We have fun at work and a human approach while performing.  When you work with us, you’ll enjoy a diverse group of people who value working together. You will enjoy an open and inclusive culture where you can be yourself. At IKEA we always do our jobs knowing that we can achieve great things when many people work together. IKEA started its operation in Greece through House Market, a member of Fourlis Group of Companies, and counts 5 stores in Greece (Athens, Thessaloniki, Larissa, and Ioannina), 1 in Cyprus (Nicosia) and 1 in Bulgaria (Sofia). IKEA – House Market also operates 7 Pick-Up-Points (1 in Rhodes, 1 in Patra, 1 in Chania, 1 in Heraklion, 1 in Komotini and 2 in Bulgaria (Varna & Burgas). Up to now we are a team of approximately 2.200 employees in all three countries we operate. If you want to find out more about careers @IKEA Greece, Cyprus & Bulgaria visit our site www.fourlisgroup-careers.gr

Name: Linhas Direitas
Company description: Cozinhas | Kitchens Roupeiros | Closets Estantes | Bookshelves  Mobiliário à medida | Custom-made

Name: Daarbak Redoffice
Company description: Daarbak Redoffice leverer alt til arbejdslivet – fra kontorartikler til print- og kaffeløsninger, emballage, gaveartikler og rengøringsartikler. Vores webshop er altid lige ved hånden, og med over 40 rådgivere, 18 butikker samt 2 logistikcentre er hurtig og kompetent levering kernen af vores DNA. Daarbak Redoffice er en del af Daarbak Group A/S som er en af de største danskejede virksomheder indenfor kontorforsyning og møbelindretning. Daarbak Group A/S har en stolt historie, som går helt tilbage til 1898. Som den er i dag, er virksomheden resultatet af mange års opkøb og den er dermed sammensat af mange forskellige virksomheder. Virksomheden har hidtil været aktive i markedet gennem tre brands Redoffice Scan Office, Mogens Daarbak og Scan Office. Ved at kombinere det bedste fra hver virksomhed har Daarbak Group A/S i dag en af de stærkeste positioner i markedet med en bred vifte af forretningsområder samt salgskanaler, som få kan matche. Med vores nye fælles navn og brand ønsker vi at være Danmarks stærkeste totalleverandør til såvel private som offentlige virksomheder. Daarbak Group A/S er en familieejet virksomhed som drives ud fra to divisioner; Daarbak Redoffice (Kontorforsyning) og Daarbak Design (Indretning & møbler). Med vores mange forretningsområder ønsker vi at hjælpe vores kunder med alt fra komplette indretningsløsninger, møbler, beplantning, kontormaskiner, kontorartikler, emballage og gaveartikler.  Find os på https://daarbakredoffice.dk/, hvor du kan læse mere og handle online.

Name: Ditre Italia
HQ Location: Italy, Tv, Cordignano, 21 Via Del Lavoro, 31016
Company description: Ditre Italia is a distinguished furniture manufacturer that has been crafting elegant and functional pieces since 1976. The company views furniture as an organic project, aiming to create coherent and inviting interiors that reflect a sophisticated yet simple elegance. With a diverse catalog that includes modern designs ranging from sofas and armchairs to dining and bedroom furniture, Ditre Italia caters to both indoor and outdoor spaces. The company's mission is to enhance living environments by providing high-quality, meticulously crafted furniture that harmonizes with contemporary living needs.  Ditre Italia collaborates with renowned designers, such as Daniele Lo Scalzo Moscheri and Stefano Spessotto, ensuring a rich tapestry of styles and voices in their product offerings. This collaboration allows the brand to appeal to discerning clients who value both aesthetics and functionality in their home furnishings. The company specializes in the design and production of high-quality sofas, armchairs, and complementary furniture pieces, with a commitment to craftsmanship and innovative design.  Targeting both residential and commercial markets, Ditre Italia's clientele includes discerning homeowners, interior designers, and architects who seek sophisticated and customizable furniture solutions. The company maintains a focus on sustainability and quality materials, further enhancing its reputation in the luxury furniture sector. Through strategic partnerships and a dedication to excellence, Ditre Italia continues to solidify its position as a leader in the industry, committed to enhancing the comfort and style of modern interiors.

Name: Szynaka Meble
Company description: Szynaka Meble is a prominent furniture manufacturer based in Poland, known for its commitment to quality and innovative design. With over 40 years of experience, the company has established itself as a leader in the furniture industry, offering a diverse range of products that cater to both residential and commercial markets. Szynaka Meble's mission is to create unique and stylish furniture that enhances living spaces while ensuring functionality and comfort. The company actively participates in industry events, such as the Meble Polska trade fair, and hosts its own furniture fairs, fostering valuable relationships with partners and clients worldwide. Its target market includes homeowners, interior designers, and businesses seeking high-quality, customizable furniture solutions. Szynaka Meble is dedicated to continuous improvement and innovation, striving to meet the evolving needs of its customers while maintaining a strong focus on sustainability and craftsmanship.

Name: Daarbak Redoffice
Company description: Mogens Daarbak A/S er en af Danmarks største leverandører af kontorartikler og forbrugsvarer til virksomheder i hele landet. Med mere end 130 ansatte og 18.000 kvm butiks- og lagerareal i 8 forskellige afdelinger er Mogens Daarbak A/S en solid og kvalitetsbevidst partner. En leverandør = en verden af muligheder Når du vælger Mogens Daarbak A/S som leverandør, vælger du en samarbejdspartner og totalleverandør, som kan tilbyde dig en vifte af unikke løsninger og muligheder.  Mogens Daarbak A/S tilbyder nemlig et enestående koncept som rummer alt fra kontorartikler, emballage, trykopgaver, planteservice, kontormaskiner, kaffebryggere, frugt, gaveindpakning, møbler & indretning til logistik & distribution.  Vi anvender udtrykket ”totalleverandør”, da vores kunder har muligheden for at vælge mellem 16.000 varer og serviceydelser. Ved at samle sine indkøb hos Mogens Daarbak A/S opnår kunderne store besparelser, da håndteringsomkostninger og antal af leverancer kan begrænses væsentligt. Kontakt os på 96 33 33 33, og hør hvilke fordele din virksomhed kan opnå i et fremtidigt samarbejde.

Name: Michael Murphy Home Furnishing
HQ Location: Ireland, Leinster, Droichead Nua, Edward Street, 0000
Company description: Since our beginning in 1974, Michael Murphy Home Furnishing has been at the heart of Irish homes, offering a blend of style, quality, and community spirit that is uniquely its own. What began as a single furniture store in Newbridge, Co. Kildare, founded by Rose and Michael Murphy, has grown into Ireland’s leading independent, family-owned furniture retailer. Over the decades, we have stayed true to our roots, embodying the values of craftsmanship, personalised service, and a deep commitment to the communities we serve.

Name: My Home Møbler
Company description: My Home Møbler tilbyder kvalitetsmøbler og en høj grad af service til overraskende lave priser. My Home lagersalgskonceptet startede med lagersalg af møbler og brugskunst fra en privat adresse i Randers. Det viste sig hurtigt, at lagersalgskonceptet var interessant for kunder i området. Derfor blev der i 2006 åbnet en My Home Lagersalg butik i bydelen Kristrup i Randers. Der viste sig hurtigt at blive behov for mere lagerplads, og med mange kunder kom også behovet for mere butiksareal, så forretningen i Randers blev flyttet til en kombineret lager og butik på adressen Nikkelvej 4 i Randers. Herefter åbnede flere My Home Lagersalg butikker rundt i landet. Der kom igen behov for mere lagerplads, og i efteråret 2009 blev lageret flyttet til Sdr. Borup ved Randers, og siden er der udvidet flere gange, med endnu større lager. Hovedkontoret samt lager har nu adresse i Fårup ved Randers. I dag er My Home landsdækkende med butikker i hele landet. Vi har lave priser pga. lav husleje, billig indretning, lav bemanding og fordi vi køber hovedparten af vores møbler direkte, uden mellemled, ved leverandører i asien og hele europa. Hos My Home Møbler kan du trygt handle såvel online samt i vores fysiske butikker. Vi er en landsdækkende kæde med 22 butikker fordelt over hele landet. Vi har Faguddannet personale, som ved hvad de handler med, mange års erfaring i salg og rådgivning, og på vores hjemmeside får du en hurtig og effektiv ekspedition

Name: Vilniaus Baldai
HQ Location: Lithuania, Guopstų Kaimas, 23 Pramonės G., lt-21148
Company description: „Vilniaus baldai“ –  140 metų patirties sukaupusi bendrovė, besispecializuojanti lengvų konstrukcijų korpusinių baldų gamyboje. Gamindami tiek paprastus, tiek daugiafunkcinius baldus, tobulumo siekiame didelį dėmesį skirdami detalėms ir jų išbaigtumo užtikrinimui. Visą bendrovės gaminamą produkciją parduodamame būtent IKEA. Dar praėjusio amžiaus pabaigoje pradėta kooperacija su Skandinavijos baldų milžine 2007 metais įgavo kertinę svarbą pastarajai tapus pagrindine ir vienintele mūsų kliente. Tikime, kad nepriekaištingos kokybės standartas glaudžiai susijęs su mūsų darbuotojų emocine gerove, todėl ypač vertiname skaidrumą ir savitarpio pagarbą.

Name: Rauch Möbelwerke GmbH
Company description: Rauch Möbelwerke GmbH is a leading European provider of wardrobe and bedroom furniture, renowned for its commitment to quality and sustainability. The company focuses on creating stylish and functional furniture solutions that cater to diverse customer needs, ensuring that every piece is designed with both aesthetics and practicality in mind. With a mission to enhance living spaces, Rauch Möbelwerke aims to provide innovative products that reflect modern design trends while promoting environmentally friendly practices. The company serves a wide range of clients, including individual consumers and retail partners, and is dedicated to maintaining strong relationships with its stakeholders. Through its extensive product offerings, Rauch Möbelwerke targets a market that values both style and sustainability in home furnishings.

Name: Office 1 / Panda Coop.
Company description: Office 1 е българска марка, лидер в офис продуктите, хартия, технологии и аксесоари, тонери и мастило, мебели, почистващи материали, луксозни продукти и Copy&Print услуги. С повече от 110 000 продукта в портфолиото си, 18 000 от които налични на склад, Office 1 предлага всичко, от което един офис се нуждае. Организацията е основана през 1998 година като мастър франчайз. Днес Office 1 разполага с огромна мрежа франчайзи в страната. С над 23 години опит в предлагането на качествени продукти и услуги, марката се е превърнала в синоним на верен партньор за нашите клиенти. Office 1 дава предложения, които са B2B и B2C насочени. Тук сме да помогнем. Ние знаем как. Нека ви покажем защо! --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- Office 1 is a leading company in the Bulgarian market for providing office products and supplies, paper, technology and accessories, toner and ink, furniture, cleaning supplies, luxury items and copy & print services. With a portfolio of more than 110 000 products, 18 000 of which available in stock, Office 1 offers everything an office could possibly need. The organisation was founded in 1998 as a master franchise company. Today, Office 1 has a vast network of sub-franchisees in the country. During these 23 years of experience in inspiring clients and providing high quality products and services, the brand has become a synonym of a trusted partner to our customers. Office 1 offers overall solutions that are B2B as well as B2C oriented. We are here to help. We know how. Let us show you why!

Name: La Tienda HOME
Company description: La Tienda HOME es una empresa especializada en la venta de muebles y productos de descanso, que ofrece una amplia gama de sofás, colchones, sillones y accesorios relacionados. Con un enfoque en la calidad y el confort, su misión es proporcionar a los clientes un espacio donde puedan encontrar soluciones de descanso que se adapten a sus necesidades y estilos de vida. La Tienda HOME se destaca por su atención al cliente, brindando asesoramiento personalizado y un ambiente de compra agradable en sus tiendas, como la ubicada en Arganda del Rey.
