Su visión es convertirse en un referente en el sector del descanso, ofreciendo productos a precios competitivos y opciones de financiación atractivas, como la posibilidad de financiar compras hasta 12 meses sin intereses. La empresa se dirige a un público diverso que busca calidad y confort en sus hogares, abarcando desde familias hasta jóvenes profesionales que buscan soluciones de mobiliario funcionales y estéticas. La Tienda HOME permite a sus clientes personalizar sus sofás, eligiendo entre diferentes tapizados, colores y configuraciones, lo que les permite crear un mueble único que se adapte a sus gustos y necesidades. Además, colabora con diversas entidades financieras para ofrecer opciones de financiación flexibles, facilitando así el proceso de compra. Con un compromiso hacia la satisfacción del cliente, La Tienda HOME también proporciona servicios adicionales como entrega gratuita y montaje, priorizando la comodidad y la experiencia de compra. La empresa se enorgullece de ofrecer productos de alta calidad a precios accesibles, asegurando que "barato" no signifique "de baja calidad". En resumen, La Tienda HOME se posiciona como una opción confiable para aquellos que buscan mejorar su espacio de descanso y disfrutar de un ambiente acogedor en sus hogares.

Name: Loods 5
Company description: Loods 5 is a prominent retail company specializing in interior design and home furnishings, offering a diverse selection of over 300 brands. With a mission to provide quality products that enhance living spaces, Loods 5 operates both online and through five physical stores located in Amersfoort, Duiven, Maastricht, Sliedrecht, and Zaandam. The company prides itself on customer satisfaction, offering free shipping for online orders and a money-back guarantee for unsatisfied customers. Loods 5 caters to a wide range of clients, from design enthusiasts to everyday consumers looking to elevate their home decor. By collaborating with various interior brands and maintaining a strong online presence, Loods 5 aims to inspire and assist customers in creating their ideal living environments.

Name: Chateau D'Ax spa
Company description: Chateau D'Ax is a renowned Italian company specializing in the design and manufacturing of high-quality furniture, including sofas, beds, and complete home furnishings. With a commitment to excellence, the company emphasizes comfort, style, and innovative design, offering products that reflect the essence of Italian craftsmanship. Chateau D'Ax aims to enhance the living experience of its clients by providing elegant and functional solutions for their homes. The company caters to a diverse clientele, including homeowners and interior designers, and partners with various retailers to reach a broader market. With ongoing promotions and discounts, Chateau D'Ax strives to make luxury and comfort accessible to a wider audience, reinforcing its position as a leader in the furniture industry.

Name: GoGift
Company description: GoGift is a leading provider in the B2B gift card market, specializing in offering a diverse range of gift card solutions tailored for corporate gifting and employee rewards. The company's mission is to enhance business relationships through thoughtful gifting, fostering trust and appreciation among clients, partners, and employees. With a focus on the growing trend of digital payments and e-commerce, GoGift caters to a wide array of clients, including businesses looking to recognize achievements and strengthen loyalty. The company partners with popular brands such as Amazon, IKEA, and Zalando, ensuring a comprehensive selection that meets the diverse needs of the German market. GoGift's vision is to innovate within the gifting space, adapting to cultural nuances and evolving consumer habits while promoting the importance of meaningful connections in the corporate landscape.

Name: ESTEL Group
Company description: Estel Group is one of the most historical and important furniture manufacturer in Italy: the enterprise was founded in 1937 and is currently the leading Italian company in the production of office furniture.  The company operated successfully for over 40 years in the home furnishing sector and only in 1980 entered the market of office furniture: today the production of office systems is the core business of the company. Estel has always made its products entirely in Italy, thanks to two modern industrial plants with over 70 thousand square meters where more than 300 workers are employed.  Estel operates mainly in the Office Contract and also in supplies for Residence and Hotels. Major orders and references have been entrusted to Estel both in Italy (Banca Intesa, BNL, Prwc, Lavazza, Gucci, Allianz, FC Internazionale, Fastweb ...) and abroad (Roche- Abertis, Santander, HavasMedia, Ing Direct).  One of the most important recent contract - with the largest American IT company - has engaged Estel for over 5 years. Estel has collaborated with great international designers such as Cini Boeri, Oscar Niemeyer, Jorge Pensi, Karim Rashid, Ross Lovegrove, Patrick Norguet, Ora Ito, Enzo Mari... Since 2015 Estel has started developing a new attitude for workplace space planning: the Italian Smart Office concept joins different kind of products - already present in the Estel array - for the realization of an interrelated work environment; this vision is based on the Activity Based Working theory, a transformational business strategy that provides people with a choice of settings for a variety of workplace activities. Besides the offices with a fixed setting (where everyone has their own desk), ABW-offices gives the personnel an opportunity to choose a place in the office where it is most suitable for them to complete their work tasks.

Name: FEST
Company description: FEST is a contemporary furniture company dedicated to creating stylish and functional home furnishings, including sofas, tables, and decorative accessories. With a mission to enhance living spaces through innovative design, FEST strives to provide customers with high-quality products that seamlessly blend comfort and aesthetic appeal. The company offers a unique shopping experience, featuring free fabric samples and personalized interior design advice, ensuring clients can find the perfect pieces for their homes. Targeting design-conscious consumers in the Netherlands and Belgium, as well as businesses seeking stylish solutions for their projects, FEST caters to a diverse clientele.  FEST collaborates with talented designers, such as Gijs Papavoine and David Derksen, to produce a wide range of unique products that reflect modern living. The company emphasizes the beauty of materials and the interplay of light and shadow in its designs, creating elegant and timeless furniture and home décor items. Committed to quality and customer satisfaction, FEST backs its products with a three-year warranty, reinforcing its dedication to craftsmanship. By focusing on sustainability and the creation of lasting products, FEST aims to resonate with individual lifestyles while aligning with broader design trends. Through its innovative approach and commitment to excellence, FEST continues to redefine contemporary living spaces.

Name: Muebles BOOM
Company description: Muebles BOOM es una empresa dedicada a la fabricación y venta de una amplia gama de muebles, incluyendo sofás, colchones, muebles de jardín, y mobiliario para oficinas y hogares. Con un enfoque en ofrecer productos de calidad a precios directos de fábrica, su misión es proporcionar a los clientes las mejores oportunidades de compra, garantizando satisfacción y seguridad en cada transacción. BOOM se distingue por su compromiso con la personalización y la simplicidad, permitiendo a los clientes elegir entre múltiples opciones de estilos, colores y calidades. Además, la empresa se involucra activamente en iniciativas solidarias, destinando parte de sus ganancias a ayudar a comunidades necesitadas y colaborando con ONGs. Su mercado objetivo abarca tanto a particulares que buscan amueblar sus hogares como a empresas que requieren mobiliario funcional y estético, con una red de tiendas físicas en diversas provincias de España para facilitar el acceso a sus productos.

Name: Paged Meble
Company description: Paged Meble sp. z o.o. is a furniture manufacturer based in Jasienica, Poland with a wide range of traditional and modern furniture for the housing as well as HoReCa markets. We are the leading supplier of bent chairs offering products in over 50 countries worldwide via a number of distributors. Paged Meble’s furniture is characterized by unique and innovative design, variety of finishes, and high proportion of carefully selected solid wood and natural veneers.  Company’s products are manufactured in 3 plants in Poland in Jasienica (chairs, mainly bent charis), Sędziszów Małopolski (chairs and tables) and Jarocin (cabinet furniture).

Name: Salgueiro Home
Company description: Desde 1974, a Salgueiro Home consolidou-se como uma referência nacional no setor da decoração profissional. Com mais de 100 colaboradores especializados e instalações de 12.000 m² em Espinho, desenvolvemos soluções inovadoras em tapeçarias, tecidos, mobiliário e têxtil-lar para arquitetos, designers de interiores, construtores e revendedores. Ao longo de cinco décadas, evoluímos de uma empresa familiar para uma marca que alia tradição, inovação e experiência, posicionando-nos como parceiro estratégico no mercado B2B da decoração. A nossa história é marcada por solidez, visão de futuro e compromisso com a qualidade, o que nos permite responder a projetos de pequena e grande escala com a mesma dedicação. Com showroom exclusivo para clientes profissionais, um portfólio competitivo e capacidade de resposta imediata, a Salgueiro Home reforça diariamente a sua missão: apoiar profissionais do setor da decoração com soluções diferenciadoras, inovadoras e de confiança.

Name: Haco Wonen En Slapen
HQ Location: Netherlands, South Holland, De Lier, 70 Leehove, 2678 mc
Company description: Haco Wonen En Slapen is a premier retailer specializing in high-quality, customizable furniture solutions, with a particular emphasis on luxurious seating options such as the Seattle corner sofa. The company is dedicated to enhancing the comfort and aesthetic appeal of living spaces, offering a diverse range of products that seamlessly blend style with functionality. Haco's mission is to deliver exceptional comfort and design, ensuring that each piece of furniture is tailored to meet the unique preferences of its customers.  Targeting individuals and families seeking stylish and comfortable furniture for their homes, Haco provides a wide selection of materials and colors, allowing clients to create personalized furniture that fits their specific needs. The company also caters to interior designers who are looking for functional and aesthetically pleasing solutions for their projects. Haco collaborates with various partners to ensure a comprehensive offering of innovative products that meet the evolving demands of its clientele. With a strong commitment to quality craftsmanship and customer satisfaction, Haco aims to be a leading name in the home furnishings industry. The company’s extensive product range includes sofas, chairs, and various types of upholstery fabrics, all designed to enhance the home experience. Haco Wonen En Slapen is not just about selling furniture; it is about creating ideal living spaces that reflect individual tastes and preferences, making it a go-to destination for those looking to elevate their home decor.

Name: Metalkas Sp. Z O.o.
Company description: Metalkas Sp. z o.o. to firma z ponad 60-letnim doświadczeniem w branży mebli metalowych, specjalizująca się w produkcji i sprzedaży różnorodnych rozwiązań przechowywania, takich jak szafy, regały i szafki warsztatowe. Misją firmy jest dostarczanie wysokiej jakości, funkcjonalnych i estetycznych produktów, które spełniają potrzeby klientów w zakresie organizacji przestrzeni w biurach, warsztatach oraz magazynach. Metalkas stawia na innowacyjność i ekologię, oferując meble malowane ekologicznymi farbami proszkowymi oraz zgodne z normami RODO.  Klientami firmy są zarówno osoby prywatne, jak i przedsiębiorstwa, które cenią sobie trwałość i bezpieczeństwo przechowywanych przedmiotów. Dzięki współpracy z różnymi partnerami, Metalkas zapewnia szeroki asortyment produktów, które są dostępne z darmową dostawą oraz możliwością zwrotu w ciągu 30 dni. Firma oferuje również wysokiej jakości drabiny aluminiowe, które znajdują zastosowanie w domach, magazynach, warsztatach oraz biurach, koncentrując się na wysokiej jakości wykonania i zrównoważonej produkcji. Metalkas dąży do inspirowania swoich klientów oraz wyznaczania trendów w organizacji przestrzeni, a także współpracuje z influencerami i blogerami, aby dotrzeć do szerszej grupy odbiorców. Wśród klientów firmy znajdują się pasjonaci organizacji przestrzeni, majsterkowicze, projektanci wnętrz oraz specjaliści w dziedzinie home stagingu. Dzięki swojemu doświadczeniu i zaangażowaniu w jakość, Metalkas Sp. z o.o. stała się uznawanym liderem w branży mebli metalowych w Polsce.

Name: Cotta Collection AG
Company description: Furniture stores across europe trust us and our employees in our factories, in sales and in customer service. Design, quality, service and exceptional value for money have made us one of the leading furniture manufacturers in europe.

Name: Elkor
HQ Location: Latvia, Riga, Riga, 201 Brīvības Gatve, lv-1039
Company description: ELKOR kompānija ir dibināta 1989. gadā. Šodien tā ir kļuvusi par vienu no lielākajiem uzņēmumiem Latvijā, kas darbojas vairākās tirdzniecības jomās, piedāvājot sadzīves elektroniku, apģērbus un modes preces, preces sportam, atpūtai un tūrismam, preces bērniem, mēbeles, mājsaimniecības tekstilizstrādājumus, interjera priekšmetus, delikateses. 2017. gadā ikgadējais apgrozījums sasniedza 50 miljonus EUR. Vienmēr esot vienu soli priekšā konkurentiem, ELKOR piedāvā ne tikai plašu preču klāstu, bet arī jaunus pakalpojumu standartus. Klientu apmierinātība ir pamats veiksmīgai uzņēmuma 30 gadu darba pieredzei.

Name: Rivièra Maison
Company description: Rivièra Maison is een toonaangevend interieurmerk met een sterke beleving, waar genieten een belangrijk aspect is. Het brede aanbod meubels en accessoires wordt geheel in eigen huis ontwikkeld. Elk product is uniek doordat het met de hand vervaardigd wordt in authentieke ateliers wereldwijd. Meerdere keren per jaar presenteert Rivièra Maison een nieuwe collectie, afgestemd op de seizoenen en in verschillende thema’s. In korte tijd heeft Rivièra Maison zich ontwikkeld van leverancier en verkoper van woondecoratie tot een sterk internationaal merk met ruim 600 verkooppunten wereldwijd. De collecties van Rivièra Maison zijn landelijk en eigentijds tegelijk en geven je het warme gevoel van thuis, waar je ook bent. Rivièra Maison, Home is where you can be you.

Name: Vibo Italy SpA
Company description: La storia di Vibo S.p.A. nasce grazie allo spirito di iniziativa e alla profonda passione di una giovane coppia, Luisa Nardi e Franco Bonin, i quali all’inizio degli anni ’80 decidono di avviare un piccolo laboratorio dedito alla produzione di griglie e oggetti in filo metallico. In meno di dieci anni, l’attività cresce, rafforza i legami con il territorio e assume nuove risorse. La svolta decisiva arriva però con una produzione personalizzata di accessori per uno dei più importanti esponenti del settore arredamento, aprendo la strada a numerosi altri clienti e permettendo a Vibo di affermarsi a livello internazionale. Vibo si distingue per la capacità di innovare e rischiare. Infatti, dalle prime semplici lavorazioni del filo metallico, l'azienda è ora leader nella subfornitura dell’arredo, offrendo una gamma di oltre 5.000 articoli, molti dei quali brevettati e commercializzati in più di 70 paesi. Il quartier generale di Vibo si trova a Trissino, con una superficie coperta di circa 16.000 mq. Nel 2014, l’azienda acquisisce ulteriori 76.000 mq di terreno edificabile adiacente, destinato ad ampliamenti produttivi, quali gli attuali nuovi uffici Sales & Marketing e il nuovo stabilimento per la logistica e l’assemblaggio. La ricerca continua di soluzioni innovative e l’adozione di tecnologie avanzate portano Vibo a realizzare accessori che soddisfano nuove esigenze funzionali, estetiche e qualitative, sempre all'insegna del Made in Italy. Vibo, emergendo come azienda di successo e un punto di riferimento internazionale nel settore dell'arredo, è sinonimo di eccellenza e di Design italiano. Oggi, chi acquista Vibo può essere orgoglioso di possedere un prodotto interamente italiano dal design unico e funzionale.  Scopri di più su di noi e sui nostri prodotti, tutti orgogliosamente Made in Italy.

Name: INTERTREND POLSKA Sp. Z O.o.
Company description: Produkcja naszych mebli odbywa się we Wrześni. To stąd produkty trafiają do sklepów w wielu krajach Europy. Za pośrednictwem zewnętrznych sieci handlowych meble INTERTREND podbijają gusta oraz międzynarodowe rynki, w tym między innymi: niemiecki, francuski, holenderski, duński czy szwajcarski. Wszystko zaczęło się w 1993 w prywatnej firmie Maver. Po 14 latach produkcji przedsiębiorstwo zakupione przez francuską grupę kapitałową, przekształcono w firmę Intertrend Polska. Dzięki dynamicznemu rozwoju infrastruktury, powstaniu centrum logistycznego i zbudowaniu stabilnego zespołu w lipcu 2019 zostaliśmy częścią portugalskiej Aquinos Group.

Name: ROLLER GmbH & Co. KG
HQ Location: Germany, North Rhine-westphalia, Gelsenkirchen, 72 Willy-brandt Allee, 45891
Company description: ROLLER GmbH & Co. KG is a prominent family-owned company based in Germany, specializing in the retail of quality furniture and home decor at affordable prices. The company’s mission is centered around customer satisfaction, providing a wide range of products for immediate purchase, which allows customers to create stylish and functional living spaces without exceeding their budgets. With over 100 stores across Germany, ROLLER caters to a diverse clientele, including families and individuals seeking both comfort and style in their home furnishings.  The product offerings at ROLLER include a variety of items such as sofas, beds, and lounge furniture, all designed to meet the needs of modern living. ROLLER is committed to sustainability, utilizing renewable resources and promoting eco-friendly practices in its product lines, reflecting a dedication to environmental responsibility. The company fosters a culture of teamwork and open communication among its employees, which contributes to a positive work environment and enhances the quality of service provided to customers. In addition to its extensive inventory, ROLLER partners with various suppliers to ensure a robust selection of high-quality items at competitive prices. The company also emphasizes accessibility, offering options for both delivery and in-store pickup to accommodate the diverse needs of its target market. Through its commitment to quality, affordability, and customer satisfaction, ROLLER GmbH & Co. KG continues to establish itself as a leading retailer in the furniture and home decor industry in Germany.

Name: Vellea Global
HQ Location: Bulgaria, Sofia-capital, Sofia, 106 A Ul. "okolovrasten Pat"
Company description: Вече повече от 30 години “Мебели Виденов“ е лидер в производството и търговията на мебели с разнообразен асортимент за дома, офиса и хотела. През последните години се утвърждава като водещ бранд и заема една от лидерските позиции в страната, което е безспорен успех за българска компания. Компанията разполага със собствена логистична мрежа, подсигурена от добре развити логистични центрове, с цел бърза доставка до всеки дом. Едно от основните предимства на “Мебели Виденов” е стремежът да е максимално близо до своите клиенти, като към настоящия момент компанията разполага с 45 търговски обекта в България. Успоредно с мащабната търговска мрежа, компанията е лидер на пазара в онлайн търговията с мебели. Освен на територията на България, компанията развива дейността си и на пазарите в Гърция, Румъния, Северна Македония и Молдова под марката Vellea Home, а през 2024 година откри първите си шоуруми в Скопие и Констанца. “Мебели Виденов” предоставя широки възможности на служителите си в професионалното им развитие - динамична и предизвикателна работна среда и широк спектър професии в редица области. В стремежа да налага позицията си на желан работодател, компанията развива работна среда, която привлича и развива качествените служители. Базите на компанията са оборудвани модерно и високо технологично с всички необходими удобства за тях. Модерната производствена база на компанията, е обезпечена с високотехнологично оборудване и квалифицирани кадри. Мисията ни е устойчив и качествен растеж чрез инвестиция в нашите служители. В компанията работят над 1700 служители, в повече от 50 различни локации, а тяхната средна възраст е 38 години.

Name: Hevea Outdoor Furniture
Company description: We are a leading outdoor furniture manufacturer in Spain and Europe, with a solid track record of over 25 years in the industry. We pride ourselves on offering exceptional solutions for outdoor spaces, dedicated to enhancing outdoor environments and experiences. At Hevea, we specialise in serving the professional market, working closely with furniture shops, decorators, developers, hotel chains and hospitality businesses, among others. Our passion lies in the creation and implementation of tailor-made projects that not only meet, but exceed our clients' expectations. We cover in-house and under our full supervision all phases of design, production, bespoke production, painting and upholstery manufacturing. All of this within 10 days, always committed to a process of continuous innovation. At Hevea, we control the entire production process. From the reception of the raw material: aluminium, sponges, fabrics... as well as the production process and its subsequent dispatch to the place of destination of the goods. All this allows us to guarantee a wide variety of options adapted to the needs of our customers, a permanent stock and an exceptional quality in all our products. Thanks to the end-to-end control of our production, we are able to provide a fast, decisive and efficient after-sales service. Connect with us and discover how we can collaborate to make your outdoor furniture projects a reality!

Name: Oranje Furniture Care
Company description: In addition to being a manufacturer of professional furniture care products, Oranje Furniture Care has been the service partner for both furniture stores and consumers for decades. Our motto? Your problem is our problem. As soon as a consumer buys one of our service programs when purchasing new furniture, we take care of all consumer questions and problems. That way, you never have to worry about service requests again. Leaving you with more time to make sure that people get their dream interior, because we take care of the rest. Currently we do this with over 200 employees, including more than 80 service specialists and over 50 Customer Care employees.  That’s Oranje Furniture Care, We take care.

Name: KENAY HOME
Company description: KENAY HOME is a Spanish company specializing in high-quality mattresses and home furnishings designed to enhance comfort and relaxation. With a mission to prioritize restful sleep, KENAY HOME offers a diverse range of mattresses featuring four levels of comfort, ensuring that every customer can find the perfect fit for their needs. The company prides itself on its commitment to quality craftsmanship, with all products made in Spain, and provides convenient services such as fast shipping and easy care options. KENAY HOME caters to a wide array of clients, including individuals seeking to improve their sleep quality and families looking for stylish and functional home decor. Through partnerships with various retailers and a focus on customer satisfaction, KENAY HOME aims to transform the way people experience rest and relaxation in their homes.

Name: MILOO HOME
Company description: Miloo Home is a premier furniture store located in Domoteka, Warsaw, specializing in high-quality, stylish furniture that enhances the character of any interior. The company offers a diverse range of products, including dining room sets, living room furniture, bedroom pieces, and outdoor collections, all designed to blend modern aesthetics with timeless elegance. Miloo Home's mission is to provide customers with personalized solutions, including custom-made furniture tailored to individual preferences in materials, colors, and dimensions. The target market includes homeowners seeking to create inviting and functional spaces, as well as businesses looking for ergonomic office furniture that combines style and practicality. With a commitment to quality craftsmanship and customer satisfaction, Miloo Home aims to be the go-to destination for those who value design and functionality in their living and working environments.

Name: ELTAP
Company description: ELTAP is a furniture company specializing in the design and production of modern, functional, and aesthetically pleasing home furnishings. With a mission to harmonize elegance and comfort, ELTAP offers a diverse range of products, including the versatile Inferne corner sofa and the stylish Biancco III sliding door wardrobe, both of which are designed to meet contemporary living needs. The company focuses on delivering high-quality furniture that combines practicality with unique design elements, catering to clients who value both style and functionality in their interiors. ELTAP's target market includes homeowners and interior designers looking for innovative solutions to enhance living spaces, while its partnerships with distributors ensure that its products reach a wide audience. Through its commitment to quality and design, ELTAP aims to become a leading name in the furniture industry, providing customers with exceptional products that elevate their home environments.

Name: HKLIVING
Company description: HKLIVING is a dynamic design company specializing in a diverse range of home furnishings and accessories, including sofas, furniture, kitchenware, textiles, lighting, and outdoor items. With a commitment to boundless creativity and design excellence, HKLIVING aims to inspire customers by offering versatile pieces that cater to various tastes, from bold centerpieces to minimalist finishes. The company draws inspiration from vintage markets and the rich Dutch tradition of design, resulting in collections that blend urban aesthetics with natural elements. Targeting a wide audience, HKLIVING collaborates with artists and designers to create timeless, playful designs that resonate with contemporary interiors. Their mission is to continuously innovate and provide products that not only enhance living spaces but also stand the test of time.

Name: Dica
Company description: Dica cuenta con una consolidada experiencia en la fabricación de mobiliario para el hogar, siendo líder en su sector a nivel nacional. Su colección incluye mobiliario para la cocina, sistemas para el hogar, armarios, baños y muebles auxiliares. Con este completo desarrollo de producto Dica se diferencia en el mercado gracias un producto con diseños y materiales exclusivos y con una gran capacidad de fabricación a medida. Su espíritu vanguardista junto a la calidad y versatilidad del producto busca inspirar, crear enlaces y conexiones entre los espacios y el mobiliario Dica.   En constante evolución desde 1984, Dica sigue manteniendo vivo el espíritu de empresa familiar, con un equipo multidisciplinar y la tecnología como referencia.  Dica es una marca joven, con un producto consolidado y en constante evolución. Presentes en España con más de 170 tiendas, amplía sus fronteras a nivel internacional exportando a Europa y América. Dica crea ambientes inspiradores que respiran confort y bienestar. Para ello, centra sus esfuerzos en inversiones constantes y una mejora continua de los procesos productivos para ofrecer mejor producto y servicio cada día, combinando las técnicas artesanales con la tecnología más avanzada. Gracias a estas inversiones ha logrado crear un proceso de trabajo que permite poder diseñar, fabricar 100% a medida y bajo pedido cualquier proyecto.  Dica trabaja continuamente por una sostenibilidad económica, social y medioambiental. “Creamos con nuestro equipo, colaboradores y clientes relaciones duraderas basadas en el compromiso de valores compartidos.”

Name: ESTRA
Company description: Estra nasce nel 2005 con l’obiettivo di innovare il concetto di agenzia con strategie e percorsi commerciali alternativi. L’idea di partenza è di ristabilire il dialogo tra i canali tradizionali della distribuzione e gli architetti, mantenendo sempre viva la linfa di novità e creatività, caratteristica principale delle aziende rappresentate. E così negli anni, realtà con prodotti ad alto contenuto d’innovazione e stile ma ancora poco conosciute, sono cresciute insieme ad Estra. L’agenzia è a tutti gli effetti una realtà unica, un vero e proprio “ponte” tra le aziende leader e i professionisti del settore: dagli architetti agli interior designer e contractors, ai più qualificati dealer di arredo e illuminazione. Oggi, da più di 10 anni, Estra collabora con prestigiose aziende di arredamento, illuminazione, rivestimenti e di decorazioni d’interni. Le aziende trattate (Acerbis, Arper, Fantin, Glas, Davide Groppi, GT-Design, Ilve, Minotti, Momenti e Woodskin), tutte di risonanza internazionale, hanno un forte carattere distintivo e apportano un cambiamento nell’approccio al progetto, offrendo prodotti d’avanguardia nello stile, nel design e nella tecnica. La specifica e profonda conoscenza di ciascuno dei brand rappresentati, rende il team Estra operativo e competitivo nel seguire il cliente dalla fase di ricerca, fino alla progettazione esecutiva, garantendo affidabilità, esperienza e cura dei dettagli.

Name: Vervoort Meubelen
Company description: Vervoort is inmiddels 60 jaar actief op de professionele markt en weet met haar ruime ervaring, in elke horeca-, zorg-, onderwijs- en projectomgeving de behoeftes van uw gasten, medewerkers, bewoners of leerlingen te vertalen naar een passend inrichtingsconcept.  Waar mensen wonen werken en zijn, zijn wij en geschikte partner voor inrichting. Van café en conferentieoord tot ziekenhuis en kantoor. Van stoel en tafel tot bed en stoffering. Ons uitgangspunt is de beleving van de eindgebruiker(s) te vangen in een totaalaanbod. Onze visie bij het inrichten van een ruimte gaat verder dan het vinden van geschikt meubilair voor uw omgeving. Met ons team van specialisten zijn we in staat een totaalinrichting neer te zetten. Raamstoffering, wandbekleding, vloeren, verlichting maar ook kleur, geur, vorm en materiaalgebruik maken deel uit van ons totaal inrichtingsadvies. Wij zien de uitdaging om iedereen zich prettig en op zijn gemak te laten voelen, in welke omgeving of ruimte hij of zij ook is.  Onze eigen interieurarchitecten en -stylisten verdiepen zich daarom, samen met u, in de belevingswereld van uw doelgroep. Op basis hiervan en in overleg met u wordt er een interieurconcept gecreëerd. Centraal hierbij staat het aangenaam verblijven, wonen, werken en presteren van uw gasten, bewoners, medewerkers en leerlingen. Naast styling, comfort en sfeer, kijken we met u natuurlijk ook naar aspecten als constructie, functionaliteit, vormgeving en toepasbaarheid van het meubilair. Wanneer die factoren kloppend zijn geniet iedereen optimaal van de inrichting tot in de lengte van jaren.  Gedurende het hele traject heeft u te maken met een vast team van eigen medewerkers dat u vanaf de eerste schetsen tot en met transport, inhuizing, montage en oplevering begeleidt. U bent altijd welkom in onze ruime showroom te Goirle om inspiratie op te komen doen en kennis te maken met onze brede collectie in hele diverse interieurstijlen.

Name: IKEA Baleares & Canarias
Company description: IKEA Baleares & Canarias is a leading retailer in the Balearic and Canary Islands, specializing in functional, affordable, and sustainable furniture and home products since 1981. The company is dedicated to improving everyday life for its customers by offering a diverse range of products, including furniture for every room, storage solutions, and home accessories, all designed with a focus on Scandinavian style and practicality. With stores located in Gran Canaria, Tenerife, and Lanzarote, as well as various IKEA points across the islands, the company serves a wide clientele, including families and individuals seeking stylish and versatile home solutions. IKEA Baleares & Canarias is committed to sustainability, implementing responsible practices in production and energy efficiency. The company actively engages with the community through initiatives such as children's contests and local projects, reflecting its dedication to social responsibility. The mission of IKEA is to create a better everyday life for the many people, a vision that is evident in their innovative product offerings and customer-centric services. In addition to its extensive product range, IKEA Baleares & Canarias specializes in modular furniture and home installations, providing professional services such as the assembly of modular wardrobes, kitchen installations, and bathroom fittings. This commitment to enhancing the home experience ensures that customers save time and receive quality service. The company also partners with local suppliers to offer fresh food options in its bistros and restaurants, enriching the overall shopping experience. Targeting homeowners in the Balearic and Canary Islands, IKEA Baleares & Canarias aims to be a one-stop solution for all home furnishing needs, combining affordability with quality and convenience. Through its dedication to customer satisfaction and sustainable practices, the company continues to play a vital role in the home furnishing market of the islands.

Name: EM Home Interior AB
Company description: Möbelkedja med 40-talet butiker i Sverige samt på Åland som säljer möbler och heminredning. Vi är en av de ledande heminredningskedjorna där butikerna ägs och drivs av engagerade handlare. Välkommen in på www.em.com eller till någon av våra butiker för att inspireras av våra inredningsidéer.

Name: SBA Group
Company description: SBA group is one of the largest Lithuanian-capital enterprises investing in state-of-the-art innovations to create a better environment. The activities of SBA companies focus on furniture, textile, real estate sectors ant investment management. SBA group unites 30 enterprises running in Lithuania and other Baltic and CEE countries with more than 3500 people working there. Its annual turnover was 400 million euros in 2023. More than 90 percent of SBA companies’ production is exported to 50 countries worldwide.  Invent Everyday, for the Better - this is a mission of SBA companies. Innovative solutions, modern and environmentally friendly systems help ensure sustainable business development with maximum attention for the people and the environment and minimum footprint on the planet.  The main SBA business areas: ✔ SBA Home unites furniture producers Klaipėdos baldai, Šilutės baldai, Inno Line, Visagino linija and Kauno baldai, "Innovo logistika". These factories operate in 210 thousand square meters.  ✔SBA Apparel units innovative textile companies Utenos Trikotažas and Šatrija in Lithuania and Mrija in Ukraine. 9 million meters and 3 million units of innovative textiles are created annually. Utenos and About are the B2C brands.  ✔ Innovative real estate development company SBA Urban develops commercial and residential real estate. 54 thousand square meters of commercial real estate was developed in Vilnius (Green Hall valley, Monday Office open space) and Kaunas (Kauno dokas and Business Leaders Center). ✔Investment in real estate is managed by Capitalica Asset Management which owns business centres 135 in Vilnius, Kauno dokas in Kaunas and shopping centre Luizė in Klaipėda. It also developed business centre VERDE in Riga's Skanste district. 🌱SBA was established in 1990. Its headquarters are located in Vilnius and Kaunas.

Name: Giovanni Ferrari Srl
Company description: Leader di mercato nella vendita all'ingrosso di prodotti tecnici professionali e fai da te, nasciamo nel 1973 dal piccolo business del fondatore Giovanni Ferrari che, acquistando prodotti dagli artigiani nel Nord Italia, li consegnava direttamente ai suoi clienti di Roma. In meno di 50 anni siamo arrivati a servire oltre 2.000 clienti tra Campania, Lazio, Sardegna, Toscana e Umbria, trattando 35.000 prodotti dei principali marchi nei settori di ferramenta, utensileria, serrature, idraulica, elettricità, prodotti chimici, vernici, agricoltura, giardinaggio, fai-da-te, arredamento per esterno, casalinghi e riscaldamento. Dopo vari trasferimenti in strutture sempre più capienti, nel 2014 ci siamo spostati nella nuova sede di Pomezia, progettata e costruita ad hoc per rispondere alle nostre esigenze operative, poiché logistica e servizio al cliente sono da sempre i punti nevralgici del nostro lavoro quotidiano. Tutto quello che facciamo è guidato dalla passione e dall'ambizione di poter offrire un servizio eccellente, migliorandoci di giorno in giorno e costruendo solide relazioni con clienti e fornitori poiché, come testimoniato dal nostro motto “Crescere insieme”, crediamo molto nella cooperazione come metodo di crescita.  Sulla base di questa politica di sviluppo, nel 2003 siamo entrati a far parte del CDF (Consorzio Distributori Ferramenta) la cui attività del si esplica principalmente nella creazione di linee di prodotti a marchio proprio di alta qualità e con prezzo competitivo.  Nel 2017 entriamo a far parte anche dell'EIW (European Indipendent Wholesalers), un gruppo europeo di grossisti specializzati nella vendita di ferramenta e casalinghi. Siamo orgogliosi che tale impegno sia stato riconosciuto. Nel 2017 ci siamo classificati al 1° posto per il Premio Assofermet per l’Innovazione e sempre al 1° posto per il Premio Miglior Grossista dell’anno. Nel 2019 nuovamente siamo stati insigniti del titolo di grossista più innovativo.

Name: Bloomingville Multibrand House
Company description: Bloomingville is a design company that specializes in creating charming and decorative home furnishings, including figurines, furniture, and textiles. With a mission to bring joy and a playful touch to home decor, Bloomingville focuses on crafting products that combine aesthetic appeal with functionality. Their offerings, such as the Floriella Deco figurines and the Pradi Lounge Chair, showcase a blend of vintage-inspired designs and modern comfort, appealing to a diverse clientele that values style and quality. The company partners with retailers to ensure their products reach a wide audience, targeting homeowners and design enthusiasts looking to enhance their living spaces with unique and colorful items. Bloomingville's vision is to inspire creativity and personal expression in home decor, making every space feel inviting and vibrant.

Name: METALTEX ITALIA SPA
Company description: FABBRICAZIONE DI STOVIGLIE, PENTOLAME, VASELLAME, ATTREZZI DA CUCINA E ACCESSORI CASALINGHI, ARTICOLI METALLICI PER L ARREDAMENTO DI STANZE DA BAGNO.

Name: PMC | Soluciones Para La Oficina
HQ Location: Spain, Catalonia, Sant Quirze Del Vallès
Company description: En PMC ofrecemos soluciones integrales para la oficina.  En otras palabras, ayudamos a Directores Generales, Directores de Compras, CTOs y Office Managers en su gestión de compras: material de oficina, printing solutions con servicio técnico oficial HP, Sharp, Develop y Mimaki, mobiliario de oficina y sistemas y mantenimientos informáticos.  ⭐ Desde PMC ¿Cómo te podríamos ayudar? ☞ Aportamos el conocimiento y experiencia de las mejores prácticas del sector. Queremos reducir el tiempo que dedicas a las compras de material de oficina y consumible informático, para que puedas dedicarte a tu negocio. ☞ Entregamos el material en 24h, asesorando a nuestros clientes para comprar los mejores artículos y lograr una reducción de costes. ☞ Ayudamos a las empresas de más de 50 empleados a cumplir con la Ley de Integración de personas con Discapacidad, a través de nuestro Centro Especial de Empleo IntegraPMC.

Name: Petrokov
HQ Location: Croatia, City Of Zagreb, Zagreb, 52d Mrkšina, 10000
Company description: Tvrtka Petrokov prisutna  je na tržištu više od 33 godine i bavi se prodajom opreme za centralno grijanje, vodovod, plinsku opremu, sanitarnu opremu i klimatizaciju te obnovljive izvore energije. Poseban naglasak stavljamo na sanitarnu keramiku, keramičke pločice i kupaonski namještaj koji možete pogledati u našim salonima. Potpuna posvećenost kupcima, pristupačne cijene i najbolji proizvodi domaćih i stranih brendova i danas su najvažniji prioriteti tvrtke Petrokov.  Naša misija je i poticanje svijesti o učinkovitom korištenju prirodnih resursa te popularizacija obnovljivih izvora energije. Da bi na vlastitom primjeru pokazali kako se to radi, na krovovima našeg sjedišta u Zagrebu smo 2012. godine postavili najveću solarnu elektranu u Hrvatskoj. Održivost koju promoviramo i zastupamo, esencijalna je i za naše vlastite procese, stoga sve naše zaposlenike učimo jednoglasnom širenju filozofije održivosti i potičemo ih da mijenjaju način razmišljanja o našim prirodnim resursima.  Osnovani smo 1991. godine u Zagrebu, a u narednih 30 godina, pozicionirali smo se kao jedno od 250 najuspješnijih poduzeća u Republici Hrvatskoj i kao drugo na tržištu u svojoj industriji. Od 2012. godine zajedno poslujemo s austrijskim obiteljskim poduzećem Odörfer, a od studenog 2017. sve poslovne udijele u poduzeću Petrokov preuzima austrijska obitelj Schneider. Otada, na čelu s direktoricom Simonom Zavratnik, svi zajedno „gradimo“ novi Petrokov koji je, osim na kvalitetu, dizajn i najnovije trendove u svijetu kupaonica i obnovljivih izvora energije, fokusiran i na postizanje optimalnih poslovnih rezultata, rast i širenje tvrtke kroz otvaranje novih poslovnica i nova zapošljavanja, te uvođenje vlastite robne marke Pe-Line, koja objedinjuje sve naše vrijednosti, interese i djelatnosti. S preko 180 zaposlenika i u 9 poslovnica diljem države, jedni smo od nacionalnih lidera u ponudi:  - sustava za grijanje i hlađenje,  - sustava obnovljivih izvora energije,

Name: Kalamazoo España
Company description: Mucho más que productos de oficina. En Kalamazoo contamos con un equipo de profesionales que trabajan con pasión para garantizarte un servicio excelente. Estamos presentes en el mercado desde hace más de 40 años, con más de 25.000 productos, servicio de entrega en 24 horas, asesores en tiempo real, garantías y obsequios de calidad. Más de 400.000 clientes han confiado en nosotros para comprar mobiliario, productos de oficina, papelería, artículos de higiene, descanso y soluciones personalizadas para todos los espacios de trabajo. ¿Por qué Kalamazoo? #Por su profesionalidad Nos comprometemos todos los días a dar un servicio de calidad ofreciendo siempre la mejor solución y asesorando sobre las opciones que pueden satisfacer las necesidades de cada uno de nuestros clientes

Name: DomésticoShop
Company description: DomésticoShop is a premier online retailer based in Hospitalet de Llobregat, Spain, specializing in contemporary home furnishings and decor. The company offers a diverse range of products, including furniture, lighting, and accessories for both indoor and outdoor spaces, aimed at enhancing the aesthetic and functionality of living environments. With a mission to create inviting and organized spaces, DomésticoShop is dedicated to providing stylish and functional design solutions that cater to modern lifestyles. The company serves a broad clientele, including individual consumers, interior designers, and professionals in the hospitality sector, ensuring that its offerings meet the needs of both residential and commercial markets. DomésticoShop partners with renowned designers and trusted brands to curate a selection of high-quality items that reflect current trends and timeless elegance. This commitment to craftsmanship and quality allows the company to inspire customers to create their ideal home environments. The vision of DomésticoShop is to become a leading destination for contemporary home design solutions, making stylish and functional decor accessible to a diverse audience. By focusing on exceptional customer service and a seamless shopping experience, DomésticoShop aims to foster a community of satisfied shoppers who appreciate the art of home living. Through its innovative approach and dedication to quality, DomésticoShop strives to transform everyday living spaces into personalized havens that enhance the overall quality of life for its customers.

Name: Furninova AB
Company description: We are a major Scandinavian producer of home furniture and whole interior concepts. We started in the early 90ies, our roots are in Sweden and today our customers can be found worldwide. We design, develop, buy and produce furniture with competitive prices always keeping long-term customer relations as our core focus. For us, the customer is everything.   Furninova makes furniture with a broad international style, always paying attention to details, continuously developing comforts and searching for high quality fabrics in line with current trends. If you ask us there is no such thing as just a piece of furniture. Good furniture should be a part of your home and everyday life: an extension of your personality and very individual requirements.

Name: HANÁK NÁBYTEK
Company description: V HANÁK NÁBYTEK, a. s. se nesnažíme o nic menšího, než o hledání dokonalosti. Vše ve firmě je podřízeno snaze vyrábět nejkvalitnější nábytek. Neustále rozvíjíme své možnosti, abychom vám mohli nabídnout to nové, nejlepší, dokonalé. Stejně jako naši předkové, kteří ve 30. letech minulého století položili základy rodinné firmě, klademe důraz na preciznost řemeslného zpracování. Ve dvacetileté novodobé historii firmy se nám podařilo vytvořit z HANÁK NÁBYTEK, a. s. symbol prestiže a kvality bez kompromisů, značku která má své nezastupitelné místo nejen na českém, ale i na zahraničním trhu. Jsme pyšní na to, že patříme do elitní skupiny výrobců zcela nezávislých na nadnárodních korporacích. Nastoupili jsme cestu úplné soběstačnosti – hlavní charakteristikou firmy je téměř nulová kooperace. Postupně investujeme velké finanční částky do nákupu strojů, zavádění technologií a školení zaměstnanců s jediným cílem – absolutní spokojeností našich zákazníků.

Name: Desicor Industrias S.A.
HQ Location: Portugal, Vila Nova, 97 Rua Das Casas Queimadas, 4415-439
Company description: Experiência Há 37 anos presentes no mercado, temos hoje uma posição sólida e reconhecida mundialmente na produção de frentes para mobiliário. Da cozinha ao quarto, passando pelo escritório e sala, orgulhamo-nos de existirem nos 5 continentes, nas habitações de milhões de pessoas, portas, painéis e gavetas com o nosso selo de qualidade. Na Desicor, conjugamos as melhores tecnologias produtivas na área de lacados com o conhecimento especializado de toda a nossa equipa e o seu foco na qualidade de todas as frentes produzidas. Clientes Parceiros A parceria e o foco na satisfação de todos os nossos clientes posiciona-nos como o parceiro certo na procura de soluções, seja para frentes de mobiliário ou complementos decorativos lacados. Somos reconhecidos pela nossa ampla capacidade de resposta industrial e de inovação. Da Qualidade ao Ambiente Qualidade, Segurança e Sustentabilidade Ambiental são pilares do nosso negócio e por isso vamos sempre mais longe por nós e pelo planeta. Certificada pela ISO 9001, ISO 28 000 e FSC, a Desicor tem como prática corrente exigir mais e melhor. A boa qualidade não tem limites. O uso racional dos materiais, água e energia, assim como a reciclagem e reutilização, são processos enraizados há muito no DNA da nossa organização. Aplicamos as melhores práticas ambientais à produção, começando pela utilização de energia 100% proveniente de fontes renováveis, à seleção de matérias-primas obtidas por meios sustentáveis e respeitadores da preservação ambiental, privilegiando fornecedores que partilhem da nossa visão e modus operandi.

Name: HORST
Company description: Verpass deinem Zuhause ein Makeover – gemeinsam mit HORST! Von der Wandfarbe, über Wohnaccessoires bis zu Upcycling-Zubehör, bei uns findest du alles für dein nächstes Projekt.

Name: ENTOS
Company description: Entos is currently leading Greek brand in the domestic home furniture market actively supporting the market as well as Greek consumers. It originally started its operation in 2006 offering innovative and complete solutions in home furniture and home equipment in general. Today, being always a member of SATO group, entos renews at all levels continuing its dynamic and fast growing operation in the Greek home furniture industry. Setting as top priorities customer’s satisfaction, modern design, product and service quality and low prices, entos is entering new market segments as kids and teens furniture as well as is refreshing its existing collections (for living room, dining room and bedroom), consisting the largest and most reliable Greek brand with complete home solutions!

Name: Rudolf Henrichsmeyer Formaplan GmbH & Co. KG
Company description: Made in formaplan – Als Teil der Henrichsmeyer-Gruppe verfügen wir über rund 100 Jahre Erfahrung im internationalen Möbelbau – mit enormer Fertigungstiefe vom Rohfixmaß bis zum fertigen Möbel. Seit 2002 sind wir als strategischer Partner für IKEA im Einsatz und produzieren auf 135.000 m² Betriebsfläche am Standort Hövelhof mit mehr als 360 qualifizierten Mitarbeiterinnen und Mitarbeitern bis zu 160.000 Schubkästen, 60.000 Möbelteile und 50.000 Packstücke täglich.

Name: Kremmerhuset
Company description: Kremmerhuset er en spennende og inspirerende interiør- og gavebutikk, hvor man kan finne inspirasjon til sitt personlige hjem. Vi har 63 butikker fra Alta i nord til Kristiansand i sør og en nettbutikk. Vi har et bredt vareutvalg, og butikkene får levert nyheter hver uke, slik at man alltid finner noe nytt og inspirerende hver gang man besøker oss. Vi har et stort utvalg av puter, interiørvarer som vaser og lysestaker, små møbler og kjøkkenvarer du garantert vil ha fremme på kjøkkenbenken eller dekke bordet med. Vi utvikler nye varepakker hver sesong, i sesongens lekre fargepaletter og uttrykk som passer perfekt sammen. Det skal være enkelt å finne noe som passer akkurat din stil og som kan mikses med det du allerede har hjemme, slik at man få et trendy og personlig hjem. Kremmerhuset ble etablert i 1979. Selskapet er eid av Dalema gruppen og har hovedkontor og hovedlager på Alnabru. Vi har en stolt historie, samt over 500 entusiastiske og dyktige medarbeidere som driver redelig, lønnsomt og morsomt.

Name: Limobel Inwo
HQ Location: Spain, Castille-la Mancha, Valdepeñas, Ctra. Ciudad Real, 13179
Company description: Limobel nace en el año 2002 en Pozuelo de Calatrava, España, de la mano de la familia Martín Chacón, como tercera generación familiar en el sector del mueble, para ofrecer soluciones competitivas, funcionales y personalizadas en el mercado del mobiliario de oficina, escolar, colectividades, mobiliario para vestuario y contract. En Limobel fabricamos mobiliario para clientes con alta exigencia en calidad, plazos de entrega y adaptación a proyectos personalizados. Trabajar con nosotros es garantía de fiabilidad y flexibilidad gracias a nuestra planta de fabricación, con líneas automatizadas para mueble metálico , madera y de pintura con sistemas robotizados. A todo esto se añade nuestra infraestructura de logística propia. Estos recursos nos confieren una total independencia de proveedores externos, que nos permiten trabajar con plazos mínimos de fabricación y entrega. Contamos con un equipo humano competente y dimensionado a pedidos de cualquier volumen, además de una red comercial propia que presta apoyo a nuestros clientes a nivel nacional e internacional.

Name: Delamora
HQ Location: Spain, Madrid, Fuenlabrada, 9 Calle Del Roble, 28942
Company description: Delamora cocinas es el fruto de la colaboración de un equipo de profesionales especializados en el diseño, la fabricación y distribución de mobiliario de cocina a medida, que ha impulsado la elaboración de un nuevo catálogo de producto, acorde a las últimas tendencias en decoración y equipamiento, que posibilitan la creación de espacios singulares integrando la cocina y su entorno. Este proyecto está respaldado por una trayectoria de 40 años fabricando y distribuyendo mobiliario, y unas instalaciones equipadas con los últimos avances tecnológicos para la producción. Una cuidadosa selección de materiales, con múltiples opciones de configuración, facilita al profesional la creación de propuestas innovadoras, que encontrará en nosotros un aliado abierto a sugerencias y con gran capacidad de adaptación. Nuestros productos incorporan componentes de máxima calidad, acreditada con certificaciones basadas en rigurosos controles y pruebas de resistencia. Los procesos de fabricación son respetuosos con el medio ambiente, y la preservación de los recursos naturales para generaciones futuras. De tal forma que el producto final tenga un bajo impacto medioambiental.

Name: RANGO STUDIO S.L.
Company description: Showroom de mobiliario - Diseño de interiores y exteriores - Proyectos de Cocina - Asesoramiento en compras puntuales de muebles, iluminación y todo tipo de objetos de decoración

Name: Wajnert Meble Sp. Z O.o.
Company description: Wajnert Meble Sp. z o.o. to polska firma rodzinna, założona w 1985 roku, z ponad 40-letnim doświadczeniem w branży meblarskiej. Specjalizuje się w projektowaniu i produkcji funkcjonalnych, wygodnych oraz estetycznie wyrafinowanych mebli, które odpowiadają na potrzeby współczesnych użytkowników. Misją firmy jest tworzenie mebli, które inspirują do życia w pięknym otoczeniu, łącząc estetykę z funkcjonalnością, co pozwala klientom na urządzanie swoich domów według własnych marzeń. Wajnert Meble stawia na innowacje, zrównoważony rozwój oraz wysoką jakość, co potwierdzają liczne nagrody i rosnąca świadomość marki na rynku. Firma współpracuje z ponad 300 partnerami handlowymi i dostarcza swoje produkty do domów w ponad 22 krajach, co świadczy o jej międzynarodowym zasięgu i uznaniu polskiego designu na świecie.

Name: JENA - Nábytek
HQ Location: Czech Republic, South Moravian, Brno, 676/259 Kšírova
Company description: Jsme český prodejce nábytku s více než 20letou historií. Máme největší výběr sedaček, postelí a kuchyní. Najdeš u nás i kvalitní matrace z různých materiálů a spousty dalšího trendy nábytku, který rozzáří tvůj domov. Prohlédni si náš sortiment na e-shopu jena-nabytek.cz, nebo na našich prodejnách, které se nachází v krajských městech. Většinu zboží máme skladem a expedujeme ho 24 hodin na prodejny nebo na 44 výdejních míst po celé ČR. Naší filosofií je nabízet co nejkvalitnější nábytek za co nejpříznivější ceny. Udělej si radost novým nábytkem. Na JENA NÁBYTEK je spolehnutí!

Name: Μαρμαρίδης Έπιπλα
Company description: Είμαστε μία 100% ελληνική επιχείρηση με περισσότερους από 150 εργαζόμενους. Στηρίζουμε την τοπική επιχειρηματικότητα, κατασκευάζοντας έπιπλα σε συνεργασία με πολλές ελληνικές επιχειρήσεις - εξασφαλίζοντας εργασία σε πάνω από 300 οικογένειες.  Δημιουργούμε θέσεις εργασίας σε νέα καταστήματα. Εκπληρώνουμε το χρέος μας ως επιχείρηση με την πλήρη απόδοση του Φ.Π.Α. όλων των προϊόντων μας στο ελληνικό κράτος. Συνεισφέρουμε ενεργά στο εθνικό προϊόν με την παραμονή και φορολόγηση της εταιρείας μας στην Ελλάδα.  Στα καταστήματα ΜΑΡΜΑΡΙΔΗΣ ΕΠΙΠΛΑ, τολμούμε να ονειρευτούμε το μέλλον όλων μας στην Ελλάδα!

Name: B2B Partner
Company description: Jsme internetovým obchodem, který nabízí firmám nábytek a vybavení do kanceláří, skladů a dílen. Na všechen náš sortiment, vyjma spotřebního materiálu, nabízíme záruku 7 let. Každý měsíc u aktualizujeme nabídku produktů, které u nás můžete zakoupit ve výhodné akci 1+1 ZDARMA.

Name: Kaudex Proyectos Hoteleros & Geriátricos
HQ Location: Spain, Castille-la Mancha, Caudete, 10 Calle La Nieve, 02660
Company description: Fabricamos  y Diseñamos Mobiliario para el sector Hotelero, con una fuerte entidad propia y personalizables proyectándolos hacia una larga vida. KAUDEX  tiene un  estilo propio alejado del convencionalismo y las limitaciones de los ambientes singulares, un estilo Contemporáneo & Luxury con los cuales evolucionamos constantemente. A través de un diseño personalizado e industrializado, todos los productos están fabricados con el máximo rigor para poder ofrecerlos al amplio mercado Mundial con la más alta calidad. En KAUDEX nos avalan más de 50 años de experiencia en la fabricación de Mobiliario.

Name: Michael Guineys
HQ Location: Ireland, Leinster, Dublin, 11/12 North Earl Street
Company description: Michael Guineys first opened its doors in 1971 on Thomas Street in Dublin, offering quality discount Bedding, Curtains and Home Furnishings. In the decades since, the family-run business has quickly established itself as a leader in stocking high-quality Bedding and Accessories at affordable prices for its customers. From Egyptian Cotton Bed Sheets, soft touch Duvet Cover sets, Pillows and Blankets to Ready Made Curtains and Curtain Poles, Guineys is synonymous with great value and quality products and we pride ourselves in ensuring excellent customer service to everyone. Guineys’ success in Dublin led the company to open its first store outside of the capital on Oliver Plunkett Street in Cork city centre in 1992. Guineys has introduced Menswear, Ladieswear and a Baby & Nursery Departments in more recent times - offering the same quality of ranges as is found in our growing Bedding and Homeware sections. The move into Munster was followed by new stores in Tralee, Waterford, Limerick and then Castlebar in 2008, while the company’s online store was launched in 2012. In 2013, Guineys opened it's first store in Clonmel, Tipperary, followed by Mullingar, Westmeath. Most recently, Michael Guineys opened its doors in Kilkenny in 2015

Name: LABE
Company description: LABE, ovvero Laboratorio Belloni, nasce dal connubio d'esperienze decennali nel campo della grafica digitale e del mondo dell'arte. Offriamo un servizio professionale a 360 gradi, curando la comunicazione globale dei nostri clienti. Dall'elaborazione dell'immagine coordinata (logo, sito web, brochure, video) alla consulenza in campo artistico (arredamento per punti vendita, personal shopper, etc...).  Chiara, che quest'anno è presente con una sua opera alla Biennale, realizza dipinti, gioielli in materiali naturali e complementi d'arredo in materiali di recupero e cartapesta. Seguiamo sempre con interesse i nuovi trend nel campo del design e delle tecnologie ad esso applicate. Questo ci ha spinti a specializzarci nel campo dell'editoria digitale. Per ogni nostro progetto, ci avvaliamo di collaborazioni con professionisti nel mondo della fotografia e di sviluppatori ed analisti web che garantiscono la qualitá di tutto quello che LABE può fare.

Name: ColchaoNet
Company description: A ColchaoNet é um projeto que nasce a partir da S.S. Móvel que, desde 1980, se dedicou ao comércio de mobiliário. Atenta à evolução do mercado, em 2005, acrescenta um novo conceito de lojas especializadas no sector do Descanso, com oferta de qualidade nos seus produtos e serviços. Em 2018 passa a fazer parte de um dos maiores Grupos Nacionais na Industria de Colchões e Estofos.    Atualmente, a ColchaoNet possui uma vasta rede de 30 lojas próprias e de um e-commerce, em que é possível encontrar as melhores marcas de colchões, almofadas, camas, estrados e outros complementos de descanso.  Com as mais conceituadas marcas do mercado escolhidas criteriosamente pelo seu constante investimento na tecnologia e na inovação em sistemas de descanso. O feedback das necessidades e exigências de nossos clientes permite que estejamos atentos ao mercado e assim podemos garantir os melhores produtos.  Na ColchaoNet cuidamos do seu descanso! Website: www.colchaonet.com Blog: http://clubedosono.colchaonet.com  Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/colchaonetcom/  Youtube: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCl8LYjXm-4eoCeDokJ_zfDw

Name: Antika Mobiliário
Company description: A Antika, S.A. foi criada em 2017, pela necessidade cada vez maior de associar a marca “Antika” ao nome da empresa. Assim, a Antika surge com base na empresa Pacheco & Moreira, Lda, que possui uma presença longa e bem sucedida no sector do mobiliário nacional e internacional. Iniciou a sua atividade em 1988, dedicando-se essencialmente ao fabrico de mobiliário clássico, com o mercado nacional como horizonte. A partir de 1989 a empresa redirecionou os seus objetivos para a criação de modelos com design próprio fazendo uma grande aposta na promoção do seu mobiliário, tendo como resultados dessa aposta, a implementação dos seus modelos no mercado nacional e internacional. A sua evolução é uma história de crescimento e desenvolvimento sucessivo, baseado na capacidade de avaliação e adaptação às condicionantes externas e na estruturação de uma organização eficiente e flexível. Tentando sempre aliar o modo artesanal de construção, com a qualidade das madeiras e um excelente acabamento, a marca ANTIKA é hoje reconhecida como sinónimo de qualidade. Tendo sempre em conta um design inovador e clássico, a sua aposta são essencialmente móveis de quarto, salas de jantar e de estar.

Name: INDUFEX S.L.
HQ Location: Spain, Valencia, Beniparrell, 17 Calle Font De Penella, 46469
Company description: En Indufex S.L. nos caracterizamos por la fabricación de mobiliario en pino macizo. Con una larga experiencia en el sector desde 1990, ofrecemos diferentes catálogos de productos, apostando por la simplicidad y funcionalidad como concepto de muebles. A lo largo de estos años, en Indufex S.L. hemos añadido valores más allá de los meramente industriales, como son calidad, diseño, innovación, nuevas tecnologías, marketing y servicio.  Ello nos ha permitido evolucionar y equilibrar ese carácter más industrial de nuestros inicios con el de una empresa cada vez más comprometida con el cliente. A partir de esta evolución hemos desarrollado diferentes colecciones de mobiliario y complementos, adaptándonos tanto a las necesidades de nuestros clientes como a las tendencias del mercado, todo ello con la utilización de nuevas materias primas y acabados.

Name: Interstudio
Company description: INTERSTUDIO er et anerkendt indretningshus med over 50 års erfaring med indretning af både private hjem og miljøer til det professionelle segment. Besøg INTERSTUDIO’s showroom i hjertet af København. Tag elevatoren direkte op til showroomet på 1. sal fra Antonigade 4. Velkommen. INTERSTUDIO HOME – Cosmopolitan Living Til dig som ønsker en bolig med præg af internationalt design. INTERSTUDIO Home byder på kvalitets designmøbler til alle hjemmets rum og kompetent indretningsrådgivning med udarbejdelse både space plan og designforslag. INTERSTUDIO BUSINESS – Smart Working Til dig der ønsker mere end bare møbler til din virksomhed. Hos INTERSTUDIO Business beskæftiger vi os med indretning af alle typer virksomheder, det sig være kontormiljøer, showrooms, hotel og restauration – hvor vi kan bidrage med løsninger til alle kategorier af rum og områder. Derudover tegner og producerer vi garderobe-og køkkenløsninger til ejendomsprojekter. Vi er vant til at rådgive og være med i de mange stadier af en indretningsopgave. Vi varetager opgaver såvel direkte med slutbrugeren som med de enkeltes rådgivere; arkitekter, bygherrer og entreprenører.  INTERSTUDIO’s designer brands Helt eksklusivt finder du hos INTERSTUDIO italienske Molteni&C, hvor vi i København har en Molteni&C Flagship Store med alt fra køkkener, garderober til møbler. Herudover er vi eksklusivforhandler på to øvrige italienske superbrands, nemlig Giorgetti og Lago Design. Desuden er vi Herman Miller’s Associate Dealer i Danmark, hvorfor vi varetager distribution og forhandling. Med Herman Miller og som en del af MillerKnoll familien repræsenterer INTERSTUDIO også det britiske miljøbevidste mærke NaughtOne. Hos INTERSTUDIO finder du endvidere eksklusivt det svenske SA Möbler med løsninger til kontormiljøer og Mikomax med flexrumsløsninger ifa. møde- & telefonbokse. Vores mangeårige relation til hhv. MDF Italia, STUA og USM Modular Furniture gør os til markedets mest indsigtsfulde på disse mærker.

Name: PAPERA S.r.o.
Company description: PAPERA je již 24 let předním českým dodavatelem výrobků, služeb a řešení pro každé pracoviště - dodáme kancelářské potřeby, nábytek a občerstvení včetně úklidových a hygienických produktů pro kanceláře, školy a provozy. Naši obchodníci si zakládají na výjimečném přístupu, který našim zákazníkům napomáhá k lepším výkonům a především pracovní pohodě.  Historie společnosti se píše od roku 1994, kdy na trhu působila do roku 2000 jako sdružení dvou fyzických osob pod názvem Paper Centrum. PAPERA zaměstnává více jak 250 zaměstnanců s působností v celé České a Slovenské republice. Naše hlavní centrum se nachází ve Svitavách s pobočkami v Praze, Bratislavě a Bánské Bystrici. Chcete se stát součástí naší velké PAPERA rodiny?  Více informací naleznete na našem eshopu www.papera.cz a www.papera.sk

Name: Wopfinger Transportbeton Ges.m.b.H.
Company description: Wopfinger Transportbeton Ges.m.b.H. is a leading provider of high-quality concrete solutions in Austria, specializing in the production and delivery of various types of concrete, including specialty and eco-friendly options. The company is committed to sustainability and innovation, as evidenced by its involvement in prestigious projects like the IKEA store at Westbahnhof, which showcases environmentally friendly design and construction practices. Wopfinger's mission is to contribute positively to urban development and environmental protection through its products and services, catering to a diverse clientele that includes construction companies, architects, and urban planners. With a focus on quality and customer satisfaction, Wopfinger Transportbeton aims to be a trusted partner in the construction industry, providing tailored solutions that meet the evolving needs of its clients.

Name: PALMA Interiør
Company description: PALMA Interiør specializes in providing high-quality, sustainable home decor and kitchenware, with a focus on elegant design and functionality. The company is committed to offering products made from certified materials, such as eik and poppeltre, ensuring that their items are both beautiful and environmentally friendly. Their mission is to enhance everyday living through stylish and practical solutions that cater to both casual and formal occasions. PALMA Interiør's target market includes design-conscious consumers who appreciate timeless aesthetics and sustainability in their home furnishings. The company collaborates with reputable designers and brands, such as Studio Sagaform, to deliver unique products that resonate with their clientele. With a commitment to quality and customer satisfaction, PALMA Interiør aims to be a go-to destination for those looking to elevate their living spaces.

Name: Yllw Factory
Company description: Soeco By Yllw specializes in providing a diverse range of high-quality furniture and storage solutions, including desks, tables, chairs, and acoustic products. The company is committed to sustainability, offering rental options that help clients reduce their carbon footprint while enhancing their workspace aesthetics and functionality. Soeco By Yllw serves a broad clientele, including businesses and organizations looking for modern, ergonomic, and environmentally friendly office solutions. With partnerships with renowned brands such as Kinnarps, IKEA, and HAY, the company aims to create inspiring and efficient work environments. Their mission is to promote a sustainable approach to office design, making it accessible for all types of organizations.

Name: Svenska Hem AB
Company description: Med mer än 60 års kunskap inom möbler och inredning, och med 36 butiker från norr till söderr, kan vi med stolthet säga att vi kan det här med inredning. Hos oss möts du av personal med ett genuint intresse för design och kunskap om såväl klassiska uttryck som rådande trender. Det finns alltid någon att be om råd, oavsett om det gäller att skapa skön stämning i vardagsrummet, göra sovrummet till en vilsam plats eller köket mer inbjudande. Vår kompetens, kombinerad med din stil, skapar hemkänsla helt enkelt! Vi arbetar både med egen design och kända varumärken som står för kvalitet, hållbarhet och design. Bland våra varumärken finner du bland annat Brunstad, Bröderna Andersson, Englesson, Klippan, Jensen, Stressless och Swedese.
